WEBVTT

00:35.083 --> 00:37.083
<i>[somber music playing]</i>

00:53.041 --> 00:54.750
<i>[woman vocalizing]</i>

01:17.000 --> 01:19.000
<i>[music continues]</i>

01:23.541 --> 01:25.541
<i>-[bicycle bell ringing]</i>
<i>-[dog barking]</i>

01:37.791 --> 01:39.583
<i>[driver] First time in Croatia?</i>

01:39.666 --> 01:41.708
<i>-[woman] Yeah.</i>
<i>-This is the old city.</i>

01:43.666 --> 01:44.833
<i>It's beautiful.</i>

01:45.333 --> 01:47.333
<i>[somber music continues]</i>

02:05.166 --> 02:06.041
<i>We're here.</i>

02:20.333 --> 02:22.583
<i>Uh, in case you need a taxi</i>
<i>while you're here.</i>

02:22.666 --> 02:25.500
<i>Oh. Thank you, Zain.</i>

02:26.291 --> 02:28.500
<i>-Enjoy,</i>
<i>-Wait, I need to pay you.</i>

02:28.583 --> 02:30.250
<i>Uh, it's been taken care of.</i>

02:31.291 --> 02:33.375
<i>Oh, well, at least let me tip you then.</i>

02:33.875 --> 02:34.708
<i>Please.</i>

02:35.541 --> 02:36.625
<i>Thank you.</i>

02:39.208 --> 02:40.583
<i>You made it!</i>

02:40.666 --> 02:42.083
<i>[laughs]</i>

02:42.166 --> 02:43.583
<i>Aw, it's so good to see you.</i>

02:43.666 --> 02:45.125
<i>You too. [gasps]</i>

02:45.208 --> 02:46.833
<i>-Look at you.</i>
<i>-[laughs]</i>

02:46.916 --> 02:49.166
<i>I can't believe we're finally here.</i>
<i>We're doing this.</i>

02:49.250 --> 02:51.625
<i>I know. Come on.</i>
<i>I've been waiting to open the duty-free.</i>

02:51.708 --> 02:53.583
<i>Yeah. Oh, you waited. That's a first.</i>

02:53.666 --> 02:55.166
<i>[upbeat music playing]</i>

02:56.458 --> 02:58.041
<i>Airbnb deluxe.</i>

02:58.875 --> 02:59.916
<i>Hey, uh…</i>

03:00.750 --> 03:02.875
<i>Thanks for paying for the taxi.</i>

03:03.541 --> 03:05.333
<i>Thank Jay. It's all on him.</i>

03:07.791 --> 03:10.750
<i>Wow! Kate, this is incredible.</i>

03:12.125 --> 03:14.083
<i>Can we move in? Stay forever?</i>

03:15.583 --> 03:16.833
<i>-Okay.</i>
<i>-[Kate] Whoo-hoo!</i>

03:16.916 --> 03:18.375
<i>-[woman] That's it.</i>
<i>-[Kate chuckles]</i>

03:18.458 --> 03:20.583
<i>Never going home. Think Rob would notice?</i>

03:20.666 --> 03:22.333
<i>Probably. But who cares?</i>

03:22.416 --> 03:25.125
<i>-Hope you brought your swimsuit.</i>
<i>-Oh, uh…</i>

03:25.791 --> 03:28.625
<i>-I think I forgot.</i>
<i>-Well, you'll just have to go naked.</i>

03:33.333 --> 03:34.166
<i>Here you go.</i>

03:34.250 --> 03:35.250
<i>[glasses clink]</i>

03:36.416 --> 03:37.416
<i>-[cork pops]</i>
<i>-[Kate] Whoo!</i>

03:37.500 --> 03:39.291
<i>-[chuckles]</i>
<i>-[woman] Ooh, fancy.</i>

03:40.416 --> 03:41.583
<i>[Kate] Dom Pérignon.</i>

03:42.083 --> 03:42.916
<i>Okay.</i>

03:46.125 --> 03:47.583
<i>-Finally!</i>
<i>-[woman] Yeah.</i>

03:47.666 --> 03:48.875
<i>To weekends away.</i>

03:48.958 --> 03:50.750
<i>-With best friends.</i>
<i>-[clinks]</i>

03:51.416 --> 03:52.458
<i>[chuckles]</i>

03:53.916 --> 03:54.750
<i>Oh.</i>

03:56.250 --> 03:57.541
<i>I got you something.</i>

03:58.041 --> 04:00.375
<i>-You didn't have to get me anything.</i>
<i>-I wanted to, though.</i>

04:00.458 --> 04:02.916
<i>I just wanted to say thank you</i>
<i>for planning this whole thing.</i>

04:03.000 --> 04:05.333
<i>And I've… I've really missed you so much.</i>

04:06.541 --> 04:08.833
<i>It's beautiful, Beth. Thank you.</i>

04:11.166 --> 04:13.291
<i>[Beth] Here. I know you love black onyx.</i>

04:17.125 --> 04:18.291
<i>-[both] Oh!</i>
<i>-[bead dropping]</i>

04:18.375 --> 04:19.875
<i>-Oh my God, I'm so sorry.</i>
<i>-[laughs]</i>

04:19.958 --> 04:21.458
<i>[groans] Where is it?</i>

04:22.250 --> 04:24.291
<i>I… I got it online.</i>

04:24.375 --> 04:26.750
<i>-I can send it back.</i>
<i>-No. No.</i>

04:27.625 --> 04:28.458
<i>I love it.</i>

04:29.333 --> 04:30.333
<i>I love you.</i>

04:30.416 --> 04:31.666
<i>I love you too.</i>

04:37.291 --> 04:38.291
<i>Ugh.</i>

04:39.083 --> 04:41.750
<i>I don't know what to wear.</i>
<i>Nothing fancy enough.</i>

04:41.833 --> 04:44.333
<i>[Rob] </i>So just go in your granny panties.
You'll still look great.

04:44.416 --> 04:45.291
<i>[laughs]</i>

04:45.375 --> 04:47.708
<i>I'm so tired. I just want to go to bed.</i>

04:47.791 --> 04:49.625
<i>So go to bed. It's your holiday too.</i>

04:49.708 --> 04:52.458
<i>No, no. Kate booked a restaurant.</i>
<i>It'll be fun.</i>

04:52.541 --> 04:54.125
<i>Tell me more about Aster.</i>

04:54.208 --> 04:55.916
<i>Are you missing mommy?</i>

04:56.000 --> 04:57.541
<i>[Rob] </i>Are you missing mommy?

04:57.625 --> 04:59.333
<i>-</i>[Aster cooing] <i>Mama.</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

05:00.750 --> 05:01.625
<i>[whimpers]</i>

05:01.708 --> 05:03.625
<i>She misses your boobs, she says.</i>

05:03.708 --> 05:04.708
<i>[laughs]</i>

05:04.791 --> 05:06.458
<i>-[Rob] </i>So do I.
<i>-[Aster whimpers]</i>

05:07.333 --> 05:08.250
<i>[inhales deeply]</i>

05:08.333 --> 05:09.791
<i>[sighs] It'll have to do.</i>

05:10.500 --> 05:11.625
<i>[Kate] Here I come.</i>

05:12.375 --> 05:13.500
<i>Ta-da!</i>

05:13.583 --> 05:15.125
<i>[Beth] Wow, Kate! [chuckles]</i>

05:15.208 --> 05:17.458
<i>[laughs] What do you think? New dress.</i>

05:18.125 --> 05:21.166
<i>I went on the post-breakup shopping spree</i>
<i>to end all shopping sprees.</i>

05:21.250 --> 05:23.208
<i>-You look amazing.</i>
<i>-[Aster whimpers]</i>

05:23.291 --> 05:26.125
<i>Oh, hey, Rob. How's it going?</i>

05:26.208 --> 05:27.125
<i>-</i>Good.
<i>-[babbling]</i>

05:27.208 --> 05:29.916
<i>Oh, is that my gorgeous goddaughter?</i>

05:30.000 --> 05:31.625
<i>Aw. Hi.</i>

05:32.125 --> 05:33.791
<i>-Give her a kiss from me.</i>
<i>-[Rob]</i> I will.

05:33.875 --> 05:36.583
<i>I've got to put her down actually.</i>
<i>You guys have a good night.</i>

05:36.666 --> 05:38.625
<i>-Don't get too drunk.</i>
-We will.

05:38.708 --> 05:40.708
<i>-And we will.</i>
<i>-We definitely will.</i>

05:40.791 --> 05:41.916
<i>[laughs]</i>

05:42.000 --> 05:42.916
<i>[clinks]</i>

05:43.000 --> 05:44.625
<i>Night, sweetie. I love you.</i>

05:44.708 --> 05:46.916
<i>-I'll call you tomorrow. Bye.</i>
-Have a good time. Love you.

05:47.000 --> 05:49.083
<i>I'm half wasted already. [laughs]</i>

05:49.166 --> 05:50.708
<i>You're such a lightweight.</i>

05:50.791 --> 05:53.791
<i>Ah, if I break my neck</i>
<i>in these things, it's your fault.</i>

05:53.875 --> 05:56.291
<i>You look like a supermodel.</i>
<i>You should keep them.</i>

05:56.375 --> 05:58.291
<i>-They'll look great at the supermarket.</i>
<i>-Hello.</i>

05:58.375 --> 05:59.208
<i>-Hi.</i>
<i>-Hi.</i>

05:59.916 --> 06:01.541
<i>Oh. This is, um…</i>

06:02.958 --> 06:03.916
<i>Sebastian.</i>

06:04.833 --> 06:06.416
<i>-The owner.</i>
<i>-Oh.</i>

06:06.500 --> 06:08.833
<i>-Have you settled in okay?</i>
<i>-Yeah. Hi, I'm Beth.</i>

06:08.916 --> 06:10.333
<i>-It's nice to meet you. </i>
<i>-[car horn honks]</i>

06:10.416 --> 06:11.541
<i>Everything's great.</i>

06:11.625 --> 06:13.416
<i>Come on. Taxi's here.</i>

06:13.500 --> 06:14.333
<i>Bye.</i>

06:17.208 --> 06:18.791
<i>[Croatian tango music playing]</i>

06:19.708 --> 06:21.041
<i>[Kate] Do you know what you want?</i>

06:21.125 --> 06:23.166
<i>[Beth] I don't know,</i>
<i>but I need to eat soon.</i>

06:23.250 --> 06:25.458
<i>-[Kate] Yeah, you do. [laughs]</i>
<i>-[Beth laughs]</i>

06:27.333 --> 06:28.708
<i>Let's get oysters.</i>

06:28.791 --> 06:30.958
<i>Jesus, are they gold-plated?</i>

06:31.041 --> 06:32.875
<i>I keep telling you it's on Jay.</i>

06:33.375 --> 06:35.125
<i>He still hasn't</i>
<i>taken me off his credit card.</i>

06:35.208 --> 06:37.541
<i>I intend on discovering</i>
<i>what the limit is before he notices.</i>

06:37.625 --> 06:38.708
<i>Won't he be mad?</i>

06:39.500 --> 06:43.791
<i>With any luck, he'll have an aneurysm</i>
<i>and drop dead on top of his assistant.</i>

06:44.416 --> 06:45.958
<i>So, uh, have we decided?</i>

06:46.958 --> 06:47.916
<i>Hello.</i>

06:48.000 --> 06:52.125
<i>Uh, we'll start with a dozen raw oysters</i>
<i>and a bottle of champagne.</i>

06:52.208 --> 06:55.333
<i>-The most expensive one on the menu.</i>
<i>-[chuckles] Excellent.</i>

06:57.750 --> 06:58.916
<i>Mmm…</i>

06:59.666 --> 07:01.875
<i>No? [chuckles]</i>

07:04.750 --> 07:05.583
<i>What?</i>

07:06.166 --> 07:07.625
<i>I've been a crap friend.</i>

07:08.916 --> 07:10.791
<i>I should've been there for you.</i>

07:13.458 --> 07:15.375
<i>You had a baby. You're forgiven.</i>

07:16.500 --> 07:17.416
<i>Are you okay?</i>

07:21.333 --> 07:22.208
<i>Yeah.</i>

07:23.375 --> 07:26.000
<i>I'm fine. Couldn't care less about Jay.</i>

07:27.708 --> 07:31.083
<i>-And what about polyamory, girl? Ooh!</i>
<i>-Polyamory, huh?</i>

07:31.625 --> 07:33.875
<i>-[cork pops]</i>
<i>-I can barely manage one relationship.</i>

07:34.458 --> 07:36.833
<i>-Who's talking about relationship?</i>
<i>-[chuckles]</i>

07:38.250 --> 07:41.166
<i>Anyway, enough about me. How about you?</i>

07:41.666 --> 07:42.541
<i>[chuckles]</i>

07:43.291 --> 07:44.583
<i>How's things with Rob?</i>

07:45.083 --> 07:46.083
<i>[sighs]</i>

07:47.791 --> 07:48.625
<i>Good.</i>

07:49.708 --> 07:51.083
<i>They're rea… They're good.</i>

07:52.916 --> 07:54.625
<i>He's really great with Aster.</i>

07:55.333 --> 07:57.083
<i>Mmm, and what about with you?</i>

07:57.791 --> 07:58.791
<i>Uh…</i>

08:00.208 --> 08:01.208
<i>He's trying.</i>

08:01.833 --> 08:03.083
<i>[Kate] How hard is he trying?</i>

08:05.000 --> 08:06.166
<i>Are you getting any at least?</i>

08:06.250 --> 08:07.625
<i>Kate. [chuckles]</i>

08:07.708 --> 08:08.541
<i>[Kate] What?</i>

08:09.375 --> 08:10.625
<i>How long has it been?</i>

08:11.208 --> 08:12.375
<i>Um…</i>

08:13.541 --> 08:14.458
<i>Over a year.</i>

08:14.541 --> 08:15.375
<i>[gasps]</i>

08:17.208 --> 08:18.583
<i>Wow. Oh.</i>

08:18.666 --> 08:19.666
<i>Um…</i>

08:20.625 --> 08:22.875
<i>Isn't it about time</i>
<i>you got back on the horse?</i>

08:23.916 --> 08:26.333
<i>I… I just don't feel like it.</i>

08:26.416 --> 08:27.291
<i>Is it Rob?</i>

08:27.375 --> 08:29.625
<i>-Is he not doing it for you anymore?</i>
<i>-[Beth] It's not Rob.</i>

08:29.708 --> 08:30.791
<i>A body never lies.</i>

08:30.875 --> 08:32.583
<i>No, no, it's me.</i>

08:32.666 --> 08:33.500
<i>It's…</i>

08:34.208 --> 08:35.208
<i>It's, uh…</i>

08:35.291 --> 08:37.791
<i>-Have you thought about leaving him?</i>
<i>-What?</i>

08:37.875 --> 08:42.291
<i>If you're not happy,</i>
<i>take it from me, divorce is the answer.</i>

08:42.375 --> 08:44.625
<i>Especially when it comes</i>
<i>with a big fat alimony paycheck.</i>

08:44.708 --> 08:47.333
<i>We're just going through… [inhales deeply]</i>

08:47.416 --> 08:48.375
<i>…a rough patch.</i>

08:49.166 --> 08:50.583
<i>You've said that before.</i>

08:59.250 --> 09:00.458
<i>-Beth--</i>
<i>-[waiter] Here we are.</i>

09:01.416 --> 09:02.875
<i>-One for you.</i>
<i>-Thank you.</i>

09:05.458 --> 09:07.125
<i>[waiter] Excuse me, may I?</i>

09:07.208 --> 09:08.791
<i>Yes. Thank you.</i>

09:09.291 --> 09:11.333
<i>-Thanks a lot.</i>
<i>-[waiter] Not a problem.</i>

09:11.916 --> 09:13.875
<i>[Kate] You're such an asshole.</i>

09:13.958 --> 09:16.916
<i>Shut up. Go away. Go away.</i>

09:17.000 --> 09:19.458
<i>I'm afraid the card was rejected.</i>

09:20.916 --> 09:22.666
<i>-Oh, I'm sorry.</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

09:22.750 --> 09:23.750
<i>Okay.</i>

09:24.583 --> 09:26.750
<i>-Oh, wow.</i>
<i>-[Kate] Stop calling me.</i>

09:26.833 --> 09:28.708
<i>-One minute and, uh--</i>
<i>-Of course.</i>

09:28.791 --> 09:29.625
<i>[Kate] Bye.</i>

09:35.791 --> 09:37.000
<i>Everything okay?</i>

09:37.083 --> 09:38.208
<i>[sighs]</i>

09:38.291 --> 09:40.541
<i>-Jay.</i>
<i>-Did he find out about the card?</i>

09:41.125 --> 09:43.708
<i>Yeah. Turns out I did discover the limit.</i>

09:46.458 --> 09:47.458
<i>-[chuckles]</i>
<i>-Oh!</i>

09:47.541 --> 09:49.375
<i>Do you want me to go halves?</i>

09:49.458 --> 09:50.750
<i>No. No, no, no.</i>

09:51.541 --> 09:55.208
<i>-You get the drinks at the next place.</i>
<i>-[Beth] Kate, I'm so sorry. I'm tired.</i>

09:55.291 --> 09:57.458
<i>-And my boobs are like gonna explode.</i>
<i>-[Kate] No, no, no.</i>

09:57.541 --> 09:59.416
<i>I have to pump. They're full, and I can't.</i>

09:59.500 --> 10:02.708
<i>-And we have the bike tour tomorrow.</i>
<i>-Oh, yeah, the bike tour.</i>

10:02.791 --> 10:04.083
<i>[chuckles]</i>

10:04.166 --> 10:05.666
<i>[Kate] Oh, come on.</i>

10:05.750 --> 10:08.083
<i>Let's relive our misspent youth.</i>

10:08.708 --> 10:11.125
<i>It took me months</i>
<i>to convince you to come away.</i>

10:11.208 --> 10:12.958
<i>Who knows when we're going to do it again.</i>

10:13.916 --> 10:14.791
<i>[chuckles]</i>

10:14.875 --> 10:16.000
<i>[Kate] Come on.</i>

10:16.083 --> 10:17.583
<i>[Kate chuckles]</i>

10:19.500 --> 10:21.500
<i>[dance music playing]</i>

10:25.458 --> 10:26.291
<i>Uh…</i>

10:26.375 --> 10:28.833
<i>The entrance is just around there.</i>

10:30.333 --> 10:32.250
<i>Uh, thank you, Zain.</i>

10:32.333 --> 10:35.708
<i>Oh, wait, wait, wait. I just want to fix</i>
<i>my face and powder my nose.</i>

10:36.416 --> 10:37.333
<i>[Kate sniffles]</i>

10:38.041 --> 10:40.250
<i>-Uh, are you from here?</i>
<i>-[Zain] No.</i>

10:40.333 --> 10:41.625
<i>Syrian.</i>

10:41.708 --> 10:42.666
<i>American?</i>

10:42.750 --> 10:43.916
<i>Uh, yeah.</i>

10:44.000 --> 10:48.333
<i>California originally, but I've lived</i>
<i>in London the last 15 years.</i>

10:48.833 --> 10:51.041
<i>You left Syria because of the war.</i>

10:51.708 --> 10:52.541
<i>Hm.</i>

10:53.250 --> 10:55.041
<i>[in Arabic] Do you miss home?</i>

10:56.833 --> 10:58.041
<i>[in English]</i>
<i>Oh, you speak Arabic?</i>

10:58.125 --> 11:01.541
<i>No, not, not very well.</i>
<i>Um, just a little bit.</i>

11:01.625 --> 11:05.041
<i>I work with the Global Rescue Initiative,</i>
<i>or I used to.</i>

11:05.125 --> 11:06.166
<i>I know them.</i>

11:06.250 --> 11:07.750
<i>-[phone rings]</i>
<i>-Cool.</i>

11:09.666 --> 11:11.250
<i>Okay. I'm ready. Let's go.</i>

11:11.333 --> 11:13.083
<i>-[Beth] Okay. Thank you.</i>
<i>-Thank you.</i>

11:13.166 --> 11:15.166
<i>[dance music playing]</i>

11:17.833 --> 11:18.791
<i>Okay.</i>

11:20.291 --> 11:21.125
<i>Yeah.</i>

11:24.625 --> 11:26.208
<i>[dance music continues]</i>

11:29.500 --> 11:30.500
<i>What do you want?</i>

11:31.000 --> 11:32.000
<i>Oh, just water.</i>

11:32.541 --> 11:33.583
<i>Let me get these.</i>

11:33.666 --> 11:36.333
<i>-No, no, you get the next round.</i>
<i>-[bartender] What can I get you?</i>

11:36.416 --> 11:37.833
<i>Two gin and tonics.</i>

11:41.666 --> 11:44.333
<i>Oh my God, look over there. Hot.</i>

11:45.000 --> 11:47.500
<i>-[bartender] Here you go.</i>
<i>-We should go over there.</i>

11:48.375 --> 11:49.583
<i>-Follow me.</i>
<i>-[Beth] Okay.</i>

11:50.250 --> 11:51.291
<i>[Kate] Coming through.</i>

11:56.041 --> 12:00.458
<i>-Mind if we join you?</i>
<i>-No, I'm sure they're waiting for someone.</i>

12:00.541 --> 12:02.541
<i>No, no, please, be our guests.</i>

12:04.333 --> 12:05.333
<i>-Hello.</i>
<i>-Hi.</i>

12:05.416 --> 12:06.708
<i>-Beth. Hi.</i>
<i>-[man 1] Hey, beauty.</i>

12:06.791 --> 12:08.000
<i>[Beth] Yeah. Oh.</i>

12:08.500 --> 12:09.666
<i>-Oh.</i>
<i>-[kisses]</i>

12:10.291 --> 12:11.208
<i>Oh.</i>

12:12.541 --> 12:14.541
<i>I don't think I've seen you here before.</i>

12:14.625 --> 12:16.125
<i>I would have noticed you.</i>

12:16.625 --> 12:17.916
<i>[both laughing]</i>

12:18.000 --> 12:20.375
<i>[man 2] I love your dress.</i>
<i>You look like a disco ball.</i>

12:20.458 --> 12:21.500
<i>[laughs]</i>

12:24.416 --> 12:26.125
<i>You want to see pictures of my baby?</i>

12:29.041 --> 12:31.041
<i>[dance music playing]</i>

12:36.000 --> 12:38.583
<i>When was the last time</i>
<i>you got hit on by someone that hot?</i>

12:38.666 --> 12:40.250
<i>He's not hitting on me.</i>

12:40.333 --> 12:41.458
<i>[Kate] Yeah, he is.</i>

12:44.416 --> 12:47.625
<i>Come on, we were just saying</i>
<i>you need to get back on the horse.</i>

12:47.708 --> 12:49.166
<i>I-- I'm married.</i>

12:49.250 --> 12:51.750
<i>[Kate] So? Rob doesn't have to find out.</i>

12:51.833 --> 12:53.083
<i>Are you joking?</i>

12:54.000 --> 12:58.041
<i>One night of excitement</i>
<i>might bring you out of your rut.</i>

13:02.000 --> 13:03.416
<i>[man 1] Manhattan for the lady.</i>

13:06.291 --> 13:07.166
<i>Thank you.</i>

13:10.250 --> 13:11.125
<i>[chuckles]</i>

13:11.708 --> 13:12.541
<i>[laughs]</i>

13:15.291 --> 13:18.083
<i>We were just saying</i>
<i>how you should come back to ours.</i>

13:25.333 --> 13:27.041
<i>-[Kate] Bitch!</i>
<i>-[screams, pants]</i>

13:27.125 --> 13:28.208
<i>[groans]</i>

13:28.708 --> 13:30.166
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

13:31.333 --> 13:32.416
<i>[groans]</i>

13:34.000 --> 13:35.083
<i>[retches]</i>

13:37.125 --> 13:37.958
<i>[coughs]</i>

13:42.250 --> 13:43.708
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

13:49.958 --> 13:51.000
<i>[groans]</i>

13:51.083 --> 13:52.541
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

13:54.791 --> 13:56.791
<i>[seagulls cawing]</i>

13:59.500 --> 14:01.250
<i>[somber music playing]</i>

14:15.666 --> 14:17.666
<i>[bubbling]</i>

14:26.708 --> 14:28.500
<i>[bubbling stops]</i>

14:33.666 --> 14:34.500
<i>Kate.</i>

14:36.375 --> 14:37.875
<i>[knocking]</i>

14:44.041 --> 14:45.291
<i>[door squeaks]</i>

14:59.416 --> 15:01.416
<i>[suspicious music playing]</i>

15:03.458 --> 15:07.291
<i>[on voicemail] </i>Hi, you've got Kate,
or maybe you haven't, so leave a message.

15:08.416 --> 15:09.500
<i>[ringing]</i>

15:10.291 --> 15:11.416
<i>[chimes]</i>

15:11.500 --> 15:12.750
<i>[Beth] Hey, did you get my text?</i>

15:12.833 --> 15:15.083
<i>-What? No. Sorry.</i>
<i>-[Beth]</i> I'm really worried.

15:15.166 --> 15:17.000
<i>It's already noon,</i>
<i>and Kate hasn't come home.</i>

15:17.083 --> 15:17.958
<i>Okay.</i>

15:18.041 --> 15:21.333
<i>So she's probably gone for a coffee</i>
<i>or a wander or something.</i>

15:21.416 --> 15:23.375
<i>-Did you have a good night?</i>
<i>-</i>Yeah.

15:25.291 --> 15:26.375
<i>I did.</i> <i>I drank a bit much.</i>

15:26.458 --> 15:28.875
<i>Honestly, I can barely remember anything.</i>

15:28.958 --> 15:31.041
<i>Right. And what are you doing today?</i>

15:31.125 --> 15:32.625
<i>We're meant to be doing a bike tour.</i>

15:32.708 --> 15:36.625
<i>There you go. That's why she's vanished.</i>
<i>Should've told her it was a shopping tour.</i>

15:36.708 --> 15:39.958
<i>She… She didn't leave a note,</i>
<i>and she hasn't texted either.</i>

15:40.541 --> 15:41.791
<i>Did you have an argument?</i>

15:42.500 --> 15:44.000
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

15:46.041 --> 15:47.583
<i>-[Kate] Bitch!</i>
<i>-No.</i>

15:47.666 --> 15:50.500
<i>Then</i> <i>don't hang around waiting.</i>

15:50.583 --> 15:52.000
<i>Get out. Enjoy yourself.</i>

15:52.666 --> 15:54.541
<i>-I'll speak to you later. Yeah?</i>
<i>-</i>Okay.

15:55.416 --> 15:58.125
<i>-I'll let you know if I hear. Love you.</i>
<i>-[Rob] </i>Bye.

15:58.208 --> 15:59.166
<i>[phone chimes]</i>

16:05.333 --> 16:06.416
<i>-[Beth] Hi.</i>
<i>-Hi.</i>

16:06.500 --> 16:08.333
<i>I'm sorry to bother you. Uh…</i>

16:08.958 --> 16:10.166
<i>Have you see my friend?</i>

16:10.250 --> 16:12.291
<i>I'm looking for her. Um, Kate.</i>

16:12.375 --> 16:15.500
<i>I think she went out,</i>
<i>and I can't get a hold of her.</i>

16:15.583 --> 16:17.375
<i>She's not answering her phone.</i>

16:18.708 --> 16:20.750
<i>You haven't seen her, have you?</i>

16:20.833 --> 16:21.708
<i>No.</i>

16:23.083 --> 16:24.916
<i>Okay. Thank you.</i>

16:26.625 --> 16:30.000
<i>You're not allowed to have parties.</i>
<i>It says so very clearly in the rules.</i>

16:31.958 --> 16:35.583
<i>And I have to charge you</i>
<i>for the two extra guests that stayed over.</i>

16:37.291 --> 16:38.750
<i>[uneasy music playing]</i>

16:39.500 --> 16:41.333
<i>[officer] </i>What was the name of the bar?

16:41.416 --> 16:42.791
<i>[Beth]</i> I can't remember the name.

16:42.875 --> 16:44.541
<i>[officer] Okay, let me see her photo.</i>

16:53.250 --> 16:55.625
<i>So you brought two men back</i>
<i>to your apartment.</i>

16:56.166 --> 16:58.625
<i>-And you don't remember their names.</i>
<i>-[Beth] Well…</i>

17:00.000 --> 17:01.333
<i>No, I don't--</i>

17:01.416 --> 17:04.458
<i>-Had you been drinking?</i>
<i>-[chuckles] Yeah, a little.</i>

17:04.541 --> 17:07.000
<i>More than a little</i>
<i>if you don't remember anything.</i>

17:07.083 --> 17:09.583
<i>I'm… I'm just not used to drinking,</i>
<i>that's all.</i>

17:09.666 --> 17:13.041
<i>I… I just had a baby. So…</i>

17:13.125 --> 17:17.333
<i>Okay, your friend</i>
<i>probably go out clubbing or to a bar.</i>

17:17.416 --> 17:18.250
<i>[scoffs]</i>

17:18.333 --> 17:20.458
<i>No, uh, we're here together.</i>

17:20.541 --> 17:23.541
<i>So we're supposed to be doing things,</i>
<i>sightseeing and…</i>

17:23.625 --> 17:24.541
<i>[sighs]</i>

17:24.625 --> 17:26.416
<i>She's not answering her phone.</i>

17:28.125 --> 17:29.250
<i>I think I found blood.</i>

17:34.375 --> 17:37.291
<i>Did you check the hospitals?</i>
<i>Maybe she had an accident.</i>

17:37.375 --> 17:40.708
<i>Yeah. I did, but there's no record</i>
<i>of her being admitted.</i>

17:41.541 --> 17:42.916
<i>[woman] Is everything okay?</i>

17:43.666 --> 17:45.666
<i>[in Croatian] Yeah. Some tourist.</i>

17:46.791 --> 17:50.375
<i>[scoffs] Her friend ditched her</i>
<i>for some guy, and she's upset.</i>

17:50.458 --> 17:53.875
<i>[in English] Does she have her bag</i>
<i>with her? Her wallet, her passport, keys?</i>

17:53.958 --> 17:55.500
<i>Yes. I checked.</i>

17:55.583 --> 17:57.416
<i>[in Croatian] I can handle it.</i>

18:03.166 --> 18:05.041
<i>[in English] Can I file</i>
<i>a missing persons report?</i>

18:05.125 --> 18:08.750
<i>No, you can't</i>
<i>because you need to wait 24 hours.</i>

18:08.833 --> 18:10.750
<i>Most people show up before then.</i>

18:12.125 --> 18:13.708
<i>I'm sure your friend will too.</i>

18:14.208 --> 18:15.791
<i>[unsettling music plays]</i>

18:20.333 --> 18:21.875
<i>[line ringing]</i>

18:26.750 --> 18:27.708
<i>[Zain on phone] </i>Hello.

18:27.791 --> 18:28.708
<i>Zain.</i>

18:36.875 --> 18:40.083
<i>-Thanks for picking me up.</i>
<i>-It was close by. It's no bother.</i>

18:40.166 --> 18:42.666
<i>[sighs] I couldn't remember the name</i>
<i>of the bar last night.</i>

18:43.250 --> 18:44.416
<i>The Blue Parlour.</i>

18:44.500 --> 18:46.500
<i>[mysterious music playing]</i>

18:50.125 --> 18:51.000
<i>That's it.</i>

18:51.500 --> 18:52.666
<i>Has something happened?</i>

18:54.291 --> 18:55.791
<i>Did you lose something?</i>

18:57.833 --> 18:58.750
<i>My friend.</i>

19:02.541 --> 19:03.791
<i>[keys jingling]</i>

19:05.833 --> 19:07.041
<i>[engine starting]</i>

19:17.125 --> 19:17.958
<i>Uh, no need.</i>

19:18.833 --> 19:21.083
<i>-You want me to come in with you?</i>
<i>-No.</i>

19:21.166 --> 19:22.125
<i>[Zain] Sure?</i>

19:22.708 --> 19:23.791
<i>Yeah, it's okay.</i>

19:25.000 --> 19:25.833
<i>Thank you.</i>

19:29.000 --> 19:30.041
<i>You served us.</i>

19:30.125 --> 19:33.000
<i>We were sitting right there with two guys.</i>

19:33.083 --> 19:34.750
<i>She was wearing a blue dress.</i>

19:35.750 --> 19:37.958
<i>No, no. Sorry. No.</i>

19:38.708 --> 19:39.791
<i>What are you doing?</i>

19:39.875 --> 19:41.625
<i>Figured you could use some help.</i>

19:44.916 --> 19:46.625
<i>[speaking Croatian]</i>

19:50.916 --> 19:52.916
<i>[bartender speaking Croatian]</i>

19:57.000 --> 19:58.625
<i>Escorts? As in…</i>

19:59.541 --> 20:02.291
<i>[scoffs] I didn't know</i>
<i>that was an actual, real thing?</i>

20:03.666 --> 20:04.833
<i>I didn't hire them.</i>

20:04.916 --> 20:06.958
<i>Then your friend must have.</i>

20:07.041 --> 20:09.000
<i>No, she didn't hire them either.</i>

20:10.208 --> 20:12.583
<i>One night of excitement</i>

20:12.666 --> 20:14.625
<i>might bring you out of your rut.</i>

20:18.750 --> 20:19.583
<i>Oh my God.</i>

20:20.666 --> 20:23.916
<i>She kept going on and on</i>
<i>about how I needed to have some fun.</i>

20:25.791 --> 20:26.875
<i>I'm such an idiot.</i>

20:27.791 --> 20:29.500
<i>I wondered why he was into me.</i>

20:30.250 --> 20:32.375
<i>The barman says</i>
<i>he's seen them there a lot.</i>

20:33.250 --> 20:35.125
<i>Always with different woman.</i>

20:35.208 --> 20:36.291
<i>Tourists.</i>

20:36.875 --> 20:37.958
<i>They joke about it.</i>

20:39.000 --> 20:41.750
<i>[sighs] Does he know</i>
<i>how to get a hold of them?</i>

20:42.333 --> 20:44.750
<i>Uh, he only knew their first names.</i>

20:45.625 --> 20:46.750
<i>Mateo and Luka.</i>

20:47.625 --> 20:49.291
<i>Come on. I'll take you back.</i>

20:53.875 --> 20:55.333
<i>[Rob on phone]</i>
You went to the police?

20:55.416 --> 20:59.125
<i>I mean, this is Kate we're talking about.</i>
<i>She's not exactly reliable.</i>

20:59.208 --> 21:02.625
<i>[Beth] </i>No, no, she wouldn't do this to me.
Leave without telling me?

21:02.708 --> 21:03.541
<i>[Rob] </i>Really?

21:03.625 --> 21:06.708
<i>How many times on a night out did</i>
<i>she ditch you for a bloke she just met?</i>

21:06.791 --> 21:08.708
<i>[Beth] </i>No,
I've left her dozens of messages.

21:08.791 --> 21:10.708
<i>-Something's happened to her.</i>
-Don't be silly.

21:11.958 --> 21:15.250
<i>I've got some brilliant pictures</i>
<i>to show you of Aster by the way.</i>

21:15.333 --> 21:18.125
<i>Earlier on, we were watching</i>
The Godfather,<i> and it turns out</i>

21:18.208 --> 21:21.333
<i>she really likes the part where they find</i>
<i>the horse's head in the bed.</i>

21:21.416 --> 21:22.833
<i>[Beth laughs] </i>Great parenting.

21:25.125 --> 21:25.958
<i>I miss her.</i>

21:26.583 --> 21:27.541
<i>[Rob] </i>Are you okay?

21:28.041 --> 21:28.875
<i>Mm-hmm.</i>

21:29.875 --> 21:31.166
<i>Well, we're seeing you tomorrow.</i>

21:31.666 --> 21:33.500
<i>Do you need me</i>
<i>to pick you up from the airport?</i>

21:33.583 --> 21:34.583
<i>Oh my God.</i>

21:35.458 --> 21:37.458
<i>I can't believe</i>
<i>it's nearly Sunday already.</i>

21:37.541 --> 21:39.333
<i>-I'll have to change my flight.</i>
-You can't.

21:39.416 --> 21:40.625
<i>I've got work on Monday.</i>

21:40.708 --> 21:43.250
<i>-What about Aster?</i>
-You don't think I want to come home, Rob?

21:43.333 --> 21:44.666
<i>But Kate's vanished!</i>

21:47.000 --> 21:47.833
<i>Yeah.</i>

21:49.500 --> 21:51.208
<i>Yeah. God, of course. Yeah, sorry.</i>

21:51.291 --> 21:54.041
<i>-Do… Do you need me to come over?</i>
<i>-</i>No, It's okay.

21:55.000 --> 21:55.833
<i>I'll be fine.</i>

21:56.416 --> 21:57.250
<i>[Rob] </i>Okay.

21:58.208 --> 21:59.916
<i>All right. Just call if you need me, yeah?</i>

22:00.000 --> 22:01.833
<i>-Okay. Good night.</i>
<i>-[Rob] </i>Good night.

22:01.916 --> 22:03.125
<i>[phone chimes]</i>

22:03.208 --> 22:04.875
<i>[ominous music playing]</i>

22:12.083 --> 22:14.083
<i>[inaudible]</i>

22:17.250 --> 22:19.000
<i>-[Kate]</i> Bitch!
<i>-[gasps]</i>

22:20.125 --> 22:22.125
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

22:45.750 --> 22:47.541
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

22:54.625 --> 22:55.500
<i>Zain.</i>

22:56.375 --> 22:57.666
<i>I think I found them.</i>

22:59.000 --> 23:02.458
<i>[Zain] </i>I called and said I wanted
to hire them for a private party.

23:03.208 --> 23:04.708
<i>They're meeting us here.</i>

23:04.791 --> 23:08.083
<i>What if they don't know anything,</i>
<i>or what if they won't tell us?</i>

23:08.166 --> 23:09.000
<i>[sighs]</i>

23:09.083 --> 23:12.458
<i>-Maybe we should go to the police.</i>
<i>-No, I'll handle it.</i>

23:12.541 --> 23:13.500
<i>Don't worry.</i>

23:18.125 --> 23:19.666
<i>How'd you two meet?</i>

23:20.208 --> 23:21.416
<i>Kate and me?</i>

23:22.541 --> 23:23.416
<i>Uh…</i>

23:25.250 --> 23:26.916
<i>I was on a semester abroad.</i>

23:28.125 --> 23:29.250
<i>We were roommates.</i>

23:30.041 --> 23:32.041
<i>I met my husband Rob through her.</i>

23:34.166 --> 23:35.708
<i>We hit it off straight away.</i>

23:36.208 --> 23:37.583
<i>You and your husband.</i>

23:37.666 --> 23:39.708
<i>No, me and Kate, actually. [laughs]</i>

23:39.791 --> 23:41.083
<i>[laughing]</i>

23:41.166 --> 23:43.333
<i>We were total opposites,</i>

23:43.416 --> 23:46.000
<i>but just clicked.</i>

23:46.083 --> 23:49.166
<i>You know, right away, she's an extrovert.</i>

23:49.250 --> 23:52.041
<i>-My wife calls it </i>Carneebeh.
<i>-[Beth]</i> Carneebeh.

23:52.125 --> 23:53.208
<i>-Yeah.</i>
<i>-What is that?</i>

23:53.291 --> 23:54.666
<i>Carneebeh. </i>It's…

23:54.750 --> 23:57.416
<i>She likes to play games. [giggles]</i>

23:57.500 --> 23:59.291
<i>[laughing]</i>

23:59.875 --> 24:00.791
<i>Carneebeh.</i>

24:00.875 --> 24:02.333
<i>How did you meet your wife?</i>

24:04.041 --> 24:04.916
<i>Mina.</i>

24:05.958 --> 24:10.083
<i>She was a doctor at the hospital</i>
<i>where I was doing my nursing training?</i>

24:10.833 --> 24:11.833
<i>She's like you,</i>

24:12.458 --> 24:14.375
<i>very trusting of people.</i>

24:14.958 --> 24:17.125
<i>She believed me</i>
<i>when I say I was a nice guy</i>

24:17.208 --> 24:19.250
<i>and agreed to go out with me. [chuckles]</i>

24:25.500 --> 24:28.083
<i>Is Mina okay with you helping me?</i>

24:33.000 --> 24:33.833
<i>She's dead.</i>

24:36.916 --> 24:38.291
<i>I'm so sorry.</i>

24:38.375 --> 24:39.791
<i>[footsteps approaching]</i>

24:40.750 --> 24:41.583
<i>[Zain] Hey.</i>

24:42.083 --> 24:43.583
<i>Don't worry. I got this.</i>

24:44.375 --> 24:46.166
<i>Hi. Hel…</i>

24:47.541 --> 24:48.375
<i>[Zain] Hey!</i>

24:48.916 --> 24:49.791
<i>[groans]</i>

24:50.666 --> 24:52.166
<i>-[Beth] I'm sorry!</i>
<i>-[waitress] Heh!</i>

24:55.583 --> 24:57.166
<i>[speaks Croatian] Go!</i>

24:57.250 --> 24:58.666
<i>[frantic music playing]</i>

25:07.458 --> 25:08.500
<i>[grunting]</i>

25:11.708 --> 25:13.333
<i>[yelping, grunting]</i>

25:19.375 --> 25:20.583
<i>[grunts]</i>

25:21.791 --> 25:23.083
<i>[speaks Croatian]</i>

25:26.125 --> 25:27.125
<i>[grunting]</i>

25:27.208 --> 25:28.166
<i>[screams]</i>

25:28.250 --> 25:29.875
<i>-[Zain] Where is she?</i>
<i>-[Luka panting] What?</i>

25:29.958 --> 25:31.583
<i>-Where is she?</i>
<i>-Where's who?</i>

25:31.666 --> 25:34.833
<i>-The woman you were with Friday night.</i>
<i>-Kate! What have you done with her?</i>

25:34.916 --> 25:37.500
<i>-I have done nothing.</i>
<i>-So why did you run just now?</i>

25:37.583 --> 25:40.208
<i>-She hired us for a good time. That's all.</i>
<i>-[Zain] Don't lie to me!</i>

25:40.291 --> 25:42.500
<i>[both speaking Croatian]</i>

25:42.583 --> 25:43.541
<i>[Luka groans]</i>

25:44.500 --> 25:46.833
<i>[speaks Croatian]</i>

25:46.916 --> 25:48.833
<i>-What's he saying?</i>
<i>-[Zain] They took her handbag?</i>

25:48.916 --> 25:50.458
<i>When was the last time you saw her?</i>

25:50.541 --> 25:52.500
<i>[Luka speaks Croatian]</i>

25:52.583 --> 25:53.791
<i>[Zain] 3:00 a.m.</i>

25:53.875 --> 25:55.583
<i>What'd you do with the bag? Answer!</i>

25:55.666 --> 25:57.416
<i>[speaks Croatian]</i>

25:58.083 --> 25:59.333
<i>[Zain] They pawned it.</i>

26:02.333 --> 26:04.625
<i>Wait. Did you drug me?</i>

26:05.166 --> 26:06.875
<i>Did you put something</i>
<i>in my water at the bar?</i>

26:06.958 --> 26:08.750
<i>-[Zain] Answer!</i>
<i>-No!</i>

26:09.708 --> 26:12.708
<i>I don't need to drug women.</i>
<i>Come on. Please let me go. Okay?</i>

26:12.791 --> 26:14.166
<i>Don't tell the police, please.</i>

26:14.250 --> 26:15.750
<i>[speaks Croatian]</i>

26:15.833 --> 26:17.625
<i>Please, I'll get you the bag.</i>
<i>Okay? Please.</i>

26:17.708 --> 26:18.916
<i>I'll take you there.</i>

26:27.166 --> 26:28.041
<i>They're hers.</i>

26:30.875 --> 26:31.875
<i>It's dead.</i>

26:33.541 --> 26:35.583
<i>[in Croatian] I didn't know</i>
<i>they were stolen!</i>

26:40.083 --> 26:43.208
<i>-[Zain] You think you were drugged?</i>
<i>-[Beth] I've never been that drunk before?</i>

26:43.291 --> 26:46.291
<i>They got me a glass of water.</i>
<i>They could've slipped something into it.</i>

26:46.375 --> 26:49.125
<i>What if they drugged Kate too,</i>
<i>you know? So they could rob us.</i>

26:49.208 --> 26:51.375
<i>Why didn't they take your bag too?</i>

26:52.791 --> 26:53.791
<i>Maybe Kate drugged you.</i>

26:57.291 --> 26:58.625
<i>Why would she do that?</i>

27:00.208 --> 27:02.666
<i>Well, she did hire them</i>
<i>to have sex with you.</i>

27:02.750 --> 27:05.875
<i>[Beth] No, no. She would never hurt me.</i>

27:05.958 --> 27:07.666
<i>I know they know more.</i>

27:09.750 --> 27:11.541
<i>-[car door opens]</i>
<i>-Um…</i>

27:12.583 --> 27:14.333
<i>Maybe don't mention my name.</i>

27:15.166 --> 27:16.750
<i>I don't want to get in trouble.</i>

27:17.875 --> 27:21.000
<i>If they revoke my visa,</i>
<i>I have no place else to go.</i>

27:21.083 --> 27:21.958
<i>[Beth] I get it.</i>

27:22.875 --> 27:25.708
<i>Listen, I'm sorry</i>
<i>for dragging you into all this.</i>

27:25.791 --> 27:28.166
<i>You're not dragging me into anything.</i>

27:28.250 --> 27:29.583
<i>Stop saying sorry.</i>

27:30.250 --> 27:31.833
<i>Call me if you need me, okay?</i>

27:36.666 --> 27:37.750
<i>[car door opens]</i>

27:41.166 --> 27:43.125
<i>[uneasy music playing]</i>

27:51.583 --> 27:52.458
<i>[engine starting]</i>

27:57.208 --> 27:58.708
<i>[Beth] Well, I couldn't wait.</i>

27:58.791 --> 28:02.041
<i>And look, now I have proof.</i>
<i>Something must have happened to her.</i>

28:02.125 --> 28:04.250
<i>Let's not jump to conclusions.</i>
<i>Let's start with details.</i>

28:04.333 --> 28:08.708
<i>-Your friend's name, date of birth--</i>
<i>-No, I gave this to him already yesterday.</i>

28:08.791 --> 28:10.125
<i>You were there.</i>

28:10.208 --> 28:11.416
<i>Where's the report?</i>

28:12.333 --> 28:13.291
<i>[clicks tongue]</i>

28:13.958 --> 28:14.875
<i>Uh…</i>

28:16.083 --> 28:19.000
<i>-You didn't file it?</i>
<i>-He told me to come back in 24 hours.</i>

28:19.083 --> 28:21.416
<i>I figured her friend was out partying.</i>

28:21.500 --> 28:23.958
<i>[scoffing] They brought two escorts back</i>
<i>to their apartment.</i>

28:24.041 --> 28:26.166
<i>They were drunk. Probably high on drugs.</i>

28:26.250 --> 28:30.708
<i>No, I… I wasn't doing drugs.</i>
<i>And… I didn't know they were escorts.</i>

28:32.208 --> 28:33.041
<i>[scoffs]</i>

28:33.125 --> 28:35.750
<i>Something bad has happened to her.</i>

28:36.291 --> 28:37.375
<i>I know it.</i>

28:37.458 --> 28:39.625
<i>[Kate] </i>I don't think
they're serial killers, Beth.

28:40.625 --> 28:43.541
<i>And even if they are,</i>
<i>I don't know if I care. Look at them.</i>

28:44.458 --> 28:46.375
<i>You need to interview these men.</i>

28:47.208 --> 28:48.041
<i>I think…</i>

28:49.875 --> 28:53.291
<i>they might have drugged me</i>
<i>or maybe both of us.</i>

28:53.375 --> 28:55.208
<i>You just said you didn't do drugs.</i>

28:55.291 --> 28:58.166
<i>I… I didn't do drugs. I was drugged.</i>

28:59.000 --> 29:01.916
<i>-There's a difference.</i>
<i>-Funny you didn't mention it before.</i>

29:02.000 --> 29:03.958
<i>'Cause I wasn't sure. I'm still not.</i>

29:04.041 --> 29:05.791
<i>[in Croatian] Can you get her some water?</i>

29:07.500 --> 29:09.541
<i>Then run these names through the system.</i>

29:18.916 --> 29:19.833
<i>[sighs]</i>

29:19.916 --> 29:20.875
<i>[sniffles]</i>

29:22.208 --> 29:24.333
<i>[in English] I'm sorry about my colleague.</i>

29:26.000 --> 29:26.875
<i>I need to ask,</i>

29:27.750 --> 29:29.875
<i>is it possible</i>
<i>you may have been assaulted?</i>

29:29.958 --> 29:31.958
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

29:34.833 --> 29:37.208
<i>[inaudible]</i>

29:42.916 --> 29:46.541
<i>Well, when we're done here,</i>
<i>we'll take you to the hospital</i>

29:46.625 --> 29:48.875
<i>for a drug test and a checkup.</i>

29:50.333 --> 29:51.166
<i>Okay.</i>

29:51.666 --> 29:52.500
<i>[sniffles]</i>

29:54.750 --> 29:56.000
<i>This is a real Dior.</i>

29:56.875 --> 29:58.041
<i>It's worth around</i>

29:58.791 --> 29:59.958
<i>10,000 Euro.</i>

30:01.541 --> 30:03.666
<i>And they admitted they stole it,</i>

30:03.750 --> 30:06.125
<i>and then gave it back to you.</i>

30:09.041 --> 30:10.416
<i>[Beth] I, eh…</i>

30:11.333 --> 30:13.500
<i>I explained Kate was missing, and I…</i>

30:14.541 --> 30:18.208
<i>told them I wouldn't go</i>
<i>to the police if they gave it back to me.</i>

30:21.541 --> 30:22.541
<i>Hm.</i>

30:24.750 --> 30:28.041
<i>[nurse] Any signs of sexual assault</i>
<i>are still inconclusive.</i>

30:28.125 --> 30:31.625
<i>We'll have those results and the results</i>
<i>of the blood test within 24 hours.</i>

30:33.375 --> 30:34.250
<i>[sighs]</i>

30:34.333 --> 30:35.666
<i>[ominous music playing]</i>

30:38.291 --> 30:39.875
<i>[Beth] What do you mean, Jay?</i>

30:39.958 --> 30:41.875
<i>-</i>[Jay] <i>It's a classic Kate move.</i>
-Going missing?

30:41.958 --> 30:44.000
<i>Always has to be the center of attention.</i>

30:44.083 --> 30:46.000
<i>She wore red on our wedding day, I mean,</i>

30:46.083 --> 30:48.666
<i>should've taken that as a warning</i>
<i>of sharks in the water.</i>

30:48.750 --> 30:50.500
<i>You haven't talked to her then?</i>

30:50.583 --> 30:52.791
<i>[Jay] </i>No, not for weeks. It's been bliss.

30:53.541 --> 30:56.375
<i>-No, no, you talked to her Friday night.</i>
<i>-No, I didn't.</i>

30:56.458 --> 30:58.500
<i>She said you called her</i>
<i>about the credit card.</i>

30:58.583 --> 31:01.416
<i>What credit card? All communication</i>
<i>has to go through our lawyers.</i>

31:01.500 --> 31:05.000
<i>Look, Beth, I can actually guarantee</i>
<i>this whole disappearance act</i>

31:05.083 --> 31:06.583
<i>is a lot of bollocks, all right.</i>

31:06.666 --> 31:07.791
<i>What credit card by the way?</i>

31:07.875 --> 31:12.041
<i>What? Are you saying</i>
<i>she's… [scoffs] faking her disappearance?</i>

31:12.125 --> 31:14.083
<i>Why? Why would she do that?</i>

31:14.166 --> 31:18.750
<i>Because drama is embedded</i>
<i>in her DNA like an extra chromosome.</i>

31:19.791 --> 31:22.875
<i>She once ran off to New York</i>
<i>for a week after we had an argument</i>

31:22.958 --> 31:24.875
<i>with no word if she was dead or alive.</i>

31:24.958 --> 31:27.791
<i>All right, just trust me,</i>
<i>she likes to punish people.</i>

31:28.500 --> 31:32.208
<i>Look, I gotta go. Just call me,</i>
<i>and let me know what happens, all right?</i>

31:32.291 --> 31:33.708
<i>[line disconnects]</i>

31:40.125 --> 31:41.250
<i>[sighs]</i>

31:52.583 --> 31:53.750
<i>[line ringing]</i>

31:53.833 --> 31:54.916
<i>[sighs]</i>

31:55.000 --> 31:56.041
<i>[clattering]</i>

31:58.041 --> 31:58.875
<i>[Beth] Kate?</i>

32:03.291 --> 32:05.583
<i>-What are you doing?</i>
<i>-Checkout is 11:00.</i>

32:05.666 --> 32:06.666
<i>Oh.</i>

32:07.416 --> 32:09.041
<i>I'm sorry, I forgot.</i>

32:09.125 --> 32:10.958
<i>There are other guests arriving.</i>

32:12.041 --> 32:13.041
<i>I'll do it.</i>

32:15.125 --> 32:15.958
<i>I'll do it.</i>

32:19.916 --> 32:22.083
<i>-Your friend is still missing.</i>
<i>-[Beth] Yeah.</i>

32:23.458 --> 32:26.125
<i>-Did you go to the police?</i>
<i>-[Beth] Yeah, they're looking for her.</i>

32:26.916 --> 32:28.500
<i>I'm staying till they find her.</i>

32:30.375 --> 32:31.791
<i>-Where?</i>
<i>-[sighs]</i>

32:32.666 --> 32:33.791
<i>I'll find a hotel.</i>

32:34.958 --> 32:36.416
<i>I have a spare room.</i>

32:37.375 --> 32:38.208
<i>Downstairs.</i>

32:39.458 --> 32:40.916
<i>I rent it sometimes.</i>

32:41.500 --> 32:43.000
<i>I'll give you a discount.</i>

32:44.875 --> 32:47.333
<i>If your friend shows up,</i>
<i>at least you will be close by.</i>

32:51.958 --> 32:52.791
<i>Okay.</i>

33:00.708 --> 33:02.000
<i>[Sebastian] You're down here.</i>

33:02.916 --> 33:04.916
<i>[ominous music playing]</i>

33:24.625 --> 33:25.541
<i>Mm-hm.</i>

33:27.500 --> 33:28.833
<i>[sighs]</i>

33:30.416 --> 33:33.166
<i>Uh, there should be towels</i>
<i>in the bathroom, and…</i>

33:34.083 --> 33:36.375
<i>just let me know</i>
<i>if you need anything else.</i>

33:39.166 --> 33:40.000
<i>Thanks.</i>

33:42.375 --> 33:43.833
<i>I think you're gonna love it.</i>

33:50.250 --> 33:52.250
<i>[uneasy music playing]</i>

33:57.708 --> 33:58.791
<i>[sighs]</i>

34:06.500 --> 34:07.458
<i>[sighs]</i>

34:10.000 --> 34:11.708
<i>[line ringing]</i>

34:13.916 --> 34:16.833
<i>[on voicemail] </i>You've reached Rob,
leave me a message after the--

34:16.916 --> 34:19.666
<i>[breathes deeply]</i>

34:34.166 --> 34:35.208
<i>[sighs]</i>

34:36.208 --> 34:38.125
<i>[uneasy music playing]</i>

34:42.791 --> 34:43.625
<i>Beth.</i>

34:45.083 --> 34:47.083
<i>[soft piano playing]</i>

35:04.250 --> 35:05.291
<i>[sighs]</i>

35:19.541 --> 35:20.916
<i>[exhales]</i>

35:25.416 --> 35:26.666
<i>[Sebastian coughing]</i>

35:26.750 --> 35:28.208
<i>[piano continues playing]</i>

35:34.750 --> 35:36.250
<i>[water running]</i>

35:36.333 --> 35:37.375
<i>[turns off faucet]</i>

35:48.833 --> 35:50.708
<i>[man and woman speaking indistinctly]</i>

35:53.291 --> 35:55.000
<i>-[speaking indistinctly]</i>
<i>-[chuckles]</i>

35:55.083 --> 35:56.583
<i>[indistinct chatter]</i>

35:58.541 --> 36:00.666
<i>-[Sebastian] You helped yourself.</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

36:02.833 --> 36:03.750
<i>[sighs]</i>

36:05.250 --> 36:06.166
<i>Uh…</i>

36:07.250 --> 36:09.166
<i>Yeah. Is that okay?</i>

36:10.666 --> 36:11.750
<i>Of course.</i>

36:14.125 --> 36:16.333
<i>Is that your recording studio?</i>

36:16.916 --> 36:17.750
<i>Yes.</i>

36:18.875 --> 36:20.291
<i>I'm a composer.</i>

36:21.166 --> 36:22.208
<i>Are you hungry?</i>

36:23.166 --> 36:24.791
<i>I was about to order in.</i>

36:26.416 --> 36:27.458
<i>Uh…</i>

36:28.875 --> 36:32.166
<i>Uh, I… I was about to go out actually.</i>

36:35.416 --> 36:36.333
<i>Good night.</i>

36:42.208 --> 36:43.625
<i>Hi. Thanks.</i>

36:44.250 --> 36:45.833
<i>I had to get out of there.</i>

36:46.500 --> 36:47.416
<i>Have you eaten?</i>

36:48.833 --> 36:50.916
<i>Let's get some food</i>
<i>before we start looking.</i>

36:51.000 --> 36:53.000
<i>-I know a very good Syrian--</i>
<i>-[Rob] Beth.</i>

36:54.625 --> 36:55.458
<i>[Beth] Rob?</i>

36:57.166 --> 36:58.958
<i>Uh, what are you doing here?</i>

36:59.041 --> 37:01.541
<i>I've been calling you all day</i>
<i>to let you know I was on my way.</i>

37:01.625 --> 37:03.458
<i>-I was worried about you.</i>
<i>-Where's Aster?</i>

37:03.541 --> 37:05.458
<i>-[Rob] She's with a babysitter.</i>
<i>-Overnight?</i>

37:05.541 --> 37:09.000
<i>My parents are away.</i>
<i>Remember? In the Dordogne. She'll be fine.</i>

37:09.541 --> 37:12.458
<i>-Sorry, am I interrupting something?</i>
<i>-No. This is Zain.</i>

37:12.541 --> 37:15.750
<i>He's a taxi driver.</i>
<i>And he's been helping me look for Kate.</i>

37:16.333 --> 37:17.541
<i>[Zain] Nice to meet you.</i>

37:18.458 --> 37:19.291
<i>You too.</i>

37:21.250 --> 37:23.333
<i>-Okay, I'll… I'll go.</i>
<i>-Okay.</i>

37:23.416 --> 37:25.250
<i>Let me know if you hear anything.</i>

37:25.333 --> 37:27.500
<i>-[Beth] I will. Thanks. Sorry.</i>
<i>-Bye.</i>

37:27.583 --> 37:28.416
<i>[Beth] Bye.</i>

37:31.125 --> 37:33.291
<i>Who the bloody hell is he? [chuckles]</i>

37:33.958 --> 37:36.916
<i>-I just told you. He's the taxi driver.</i>
<i>-Who you were going to dinner with.</i>

37:37.000 --> 37:38.625
<i>Give me a break. He's been helping me.</i>

37:38.708 --> 37:43.250
<i>He… He drove me and Kate to a bar</i>
<i>the night that she went missing--</i>

37:43.333 --> 37:45.583
<i>Beth, are you kidding?</i>
<i>What if he's involved?</i>

37:45.666 --> 37:47.250
<i>[scoffs] No.</i>

37:47.333 --> 37:49.125
<i>You were just about</i>
<i>to get into a car with him.</i>

37:49.208 --> 37:51.416
<i>-You're being ridiculous.</i>
<i>-No, I'm not.</i>

37:51.500 --> 37:52.583
<i>Jesus, Beth.</i>

37:57.375 --> 37:58.500
<i>[sighs]</i>

37:59.083 --> 38:00.208
<i>[clicks tongue]</i>

38:01.208 --> 38:02.041
<i>Hey.</i>

38:03.291 --> 38:04.125
<i>Come here.</i>

38:05.125 --> 38:07.125
<i>-I'm sorry.</i>
<i>-[Beth crying]</i>

38:07.208 --> 38:08.541
<i>I am sorry, all right?</i>

38:11.583 --> 38:13.333
<i>I didn't mean to upset you.</i>

38:13.416 --> 38:15.791
<i>Why didn't you tell me?</i>
<i>I would've flown straight over.</i>

38:15.875 --> 38:17.208
<i>I couldn't tell you over the phone.</i>

38:17.291 --> 38:18.250
<i>Escorts?</i>

38:20.125 --> 38:21.041
<i>She hired them?</i>

38:21.875 --> 38:22.833
<i>[sighs]</i>

38:23.458 --> 38:26.000
<i>Do the police think</i>
<i>they're involved in her going missing?</i>

38:26.083 --> 38:27.375
<i>They don't seem to have a clue.</i>

38:27.458 --> 38:29.333
<i>And they're barely lifting a finger</i>
<i>to find her.</i>

38:29.416 --> 38:31.541
<i>[Rob] What if Jay's right,</i>
<i>and she's messing with us?</i>

38:31.625 --> 38:33.458
<i>No. I know Kate. She'd…</i>

38:34.166 --> 38:38.000
<i>She likes to be the center of attention,</i>
<i>yes, but she wouldn't do this to me.</i>

38:39.291 --> 38:40.333
<i>[phone buzzing]</i>

38:43.791 --> 38:44.625
<i>Hello.</i>

38:46.041 --> 38:48.291
<i>[foreboding music playing]</i>

38:50.625 --> 38:52.666
<i>[man]</i> She's been in the water
for some time.

38:53.541 --> 38:54.750
<i>[gasps]</i>

38:56.833 --> 38:57.833
<i>Oh.</i>

39:00.875 --> 39:01.833
<i>[Rob] It's her.</i>

39:01.916 --> 39:03.208
<i>Oh my God!</i>

39:04.916 --> 39:06.458
<i>[crying]</i>

39:09.791 --> 39:10.791
<i>[sniffles]</i>

39:13.625 --> 39:14.625
<i>She drowned?</i>

39:15.666 --> 39:18.500
<i>It's too soon to say.</i>
<i>The autopsy will tell us more.</i>

39:18.583 --> 39:21.875
<i>But you think it was an accident?</i>
<i>[sniffles] That she fell in?</i>

39:26.708 --> 39:28.583
<i>Or do you think she was killed?</i>

39:29.708 --> 39:31.833
<i>We need to wait</i>
<i>for the result of the autopsy.</i>

39:33.083 --> 39:34.916
<i>We'll be in touch when we know more.</i>

39:35.500 --> 39:37.500
<i>[sobbing]</i>

40:04.708 --> 40:05.833
<i>What are you doing?</i>

40:10.875 --> 40:11.791
<i>Couldn't sleep.</i>

40:13.375 --> 40:14.541
<i>I keep seeing her</i>

40:16.166 --> 40:17.666
<i>lying there on that slab.</i>

40:22.000 --> 40:24.625
<i>I feel bad, you know,</i>
<i>for finding her annoying.</i>

40:26.291 --> 40:27.666
<i>I should've been nicer.</i>

40:28.250 --> 40:29.791
<i>[somber music playing]</i>

40:44.833 --> 40:47.333
<i>I have to get going soon.</i>
<i>You sure you don't want to come with me?</i>

40:47.416 --> 40:49.208
<i>We talked about this. I have to…</i>

40:50.291 --> 40:52.750
<i>stay till after the autopsy and…</i>

40:54.375 --> 40:57.875
<i>-There's the arrangements to figure out.</i>
<i>-Yeah. Sorry. Sorry.</i>

40:58.375 --> 40:59.666
<i>I know. You're right.</i>

41:05.625 --> 41:06.583
<i>[Beth sniffles]</i>

41:08.250 --> 41:09.500
<i>[kisses]</i>

41:10.750 --> 41:11.666
<i>[sniffles]</i>

41:24.333 --> 41:25.833
<i>[Beth] Is the coroner certain?</i>

41:27.416 --> 41:28.500
<i>[officer] Yes.</i>

41:30.208 --> 41:31.750
<i>It's now a murder inquiry.</i>

41:32.416 --> 41:36.083
<i>They can't tell if she was sexually</i>
<i>assaulted given the state of the body.</i>

41:37.625 --> 41:40.375
<i>And the fact</i>
<i>she had sex with multiple partners</i>

41:40.458 --> 41:42.125
<i>on the night she went missing.</i>

41:53.958 --> 41:55.041
<i>Can I see her?</i>

41:57.833 --> 41:59.166
<i>I want to say goodbye.</i>

42:00.500 --> 42:01.333
<i>Properly.</i>

42:15.000 --> 42:16.166
<i>[crying]</i>

42:19.291 --> 42:21.291
<i>Can I have a minute? Please?</i>

42:40.708 --> 42:41.750
<i>[clicks]</i>

42:47.208 --> 42:48.125
<i>We need to go.</i>

43:03.291 --> 43:04.250
<i>I… I have to…</i>

43:08.666 --> 43:09.708
<i>[door closes]</i>

43:12.375 --> 43:13.333
<i>[sighs]</i>

43:13.875 --> 43:15.000
<i>[inhales deeply]</i>

43:18.583 --> 43:19.583
<i>[phone clicks]</i>

43:19.666 --> 43:20.708
<i>[sniffles]</i>

43:32.875 --> 43:33.750
<i>[line ringing]</i>

43:36.625 --> 43:39.916
<i>[on voicemail] </i>You've reached Rob,
leave me a message after the tone.

43:40.000 --> 43:41.583
<i>[beeps]</i>

43:41.666 --> 43:43.666
<i>[ominous music playing]</i>

43:47.708 --> 43:49.708
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

43:55.708 --> 43:57.541
<i>[ominous music continues]</i>

44:30.375 --> 44:31.250
<i>[knocking]</i>

44:31.333 --> 44:33.416
<i>-[officer] Everything okay?</i>
<i>-[Beth] Yes.</i>

44:36.791 --> 44:37.708
<i>[door squeaks]</i>

44:40.958 --> 44:42.625
<i>-You ready?</i>
<i>-[Beth] Mm-mm.</i>

44:42.708 --> 44:43.875
<i>Kovac is waiting.</i>

44:45.750 --> 44:46.708
<i>Screen's broken.</i>

44:53.916 --> 44:55.958
<i>[Kovac] </i>The toxicology report came back.

44:56.041 --> 44:59.500
<i>It shows high levels</i>
<i>of cocaine and ketamine in Kate's system.</i>

45:00.791 --> 45:02.541
<i>Did you know she was taking drugs?</i>

45:03.458 --> 45:04.291
<i>Yes.</i>

45:05.541 --> 45:06.833
<i>Why didn't you tell us?</i>

45:06.916 --> 45:09.291
<i>You'd already made a judgment</i>
<i>about who she was.</i>

45:09.375 --> 45:12.583
<i>I thought it would stop you looking</i>
<i>for her, and it did.</i>

45:13.833 --> 45:14.666
<i>Didn't it?</i>

45:21.750 --> 45:24.250
<i>[Kovac] The results of your blood work</i>
<i>came back too.</i>

45:24.333 --> 45:25.875
<i>They also found traces of ketamine.</i>

45:25.958 --> 45:28.291
<i>See. I… I told you I was drugged.</i>

45:28.375 --> 45:30.875
<i>[Kovac] We interviewed</i>
<i>the two men you identified.</i>

45:30.958 --> 45:33.250
<i>They deny giving you</i>
<i>any illegal substances.</i>

45:33.333 --> 45:35.458
<i>Well, they would. Wouldn't they?</i>

45:35.541 --> 45:37.333
<i>Well, they've got no priors.</i>

45:38.000 --> 45:40.625
<i>And they also have alibis</i>
<i>for the time of the murder.</i>

45:40.708 --> 45:43.125
<i>A taxi driver</i>
<i>picked them up outside your apartment.</i>

45:43.208 --> 45:45.125
<i>Their roommate can vouch for them too.</i>

45:45.208 --> 45:46.333
<i>Bad luck.</i>

45:48.833 --> 45:51.166
<i>What about Jay?</i>

45:51.958 --> 45:53.500
<i>It's Kate's ex-husband.</i>

45:54.333 --> 45:56.458
<i>She's divorcing him. Isn't that a motive?</i>

45:56.541 --> 45:57.458
<i>He's in London.</i>

45:57.541 --> 45:59.291
<i>[Beth] It's only a two-hour flight</i>
<i>from here.</i>

45:59.375 --> 46:00.541
<i>We'll look into it.</i>

46:01.791 --> 46:03.750
<i>We interviewed people</i>
<i>from the Blue Parlour,</i>

46:03.833 --> 46:06.541
<i>and several people saw you</i>
<i>and Kate arguing when you left.</i>

46:06.625 --> 46:07.875
<i>What? No.</i>

46:08.583 --> 46:09.541
<i>That's not true.</i>

46:09.625 --> 46:13.083
<i>You didn't argue with Kate then,</i>
<i>hours before she died?</i>

46:14.583 --> 46:15.500
<i>[laughing]</i>

46:15.583 --> 46:17.833
<i>[Beth] </i>They're complete strangers!

46:17.916 --> 46:19.958
<i>Relax! It'll be an adventure!</i>

46:21.916 --> 46:23.250
<i>It wasn't an argument.</i>

46:23.916 --> 46:25.250
<i>It was a conversation.</i>

46:25.875 --> 46:28.291
<i>I thought you didn't recall anything</i>
<i>about that night.</i>

46:28.375 --> 46:29.916
<i>-You were drugged, remember?</i>
<i>-[Beth] No.</i>

46:30.000 --> 46:33.375
<i>I… I passed out in the taxi,</i>
<i>but I remember some things.</i>

46:33.458 --> 46:35.166
<i>Your story keeps changing.</i>

46:36.958 --> 46:38.166
<i>What are you saying?</i>

46:39.458 --> 46:42.125
<i>You think I have something</i>
<i>to do with Kate's murder?</i>

46:44.291 --> 46:46.541
<i>Is there anything else</i>
<i>you haven't told us?</i>

46:47.166 --> 46:49.166
<i>[tense music playing]</i>

46:55.166 --> 46:56.000
<i>No.</i>

47:01.166 --> 47:04.500
<i>[officer] We need your passport</i>
<i>until we can verify your statement.</i>

47:07.291 --> 47:09.166
<i>[officer and Sebastian speaking Croatian]</i>

47:10.000 --> 47:11.916
<i>If you remember anything, call me.</i>

47:19.875 --> 47:22.125
<i>[in English]</i>
<i>Let's hope your story checks out.</i>

47:24.500 --> 47:26.500
<i>[seagulls cawing]</i>

47:30.041 --> 47:31.416
<i>Jay, you knew.</i>

47:32.083 --> 47:32.916
<i>Didn't you?</i>

47:33.000 --> 47:34.416
<i>Why didn't you tell me?</i>

47:35.125 --> 47:39.791
<i>Look, I was going to,</i>
<i>but, uh, you were about to have a baby.</i>

47:39.875 --> 47:43.041
<i>My husband</i>
<i>was having an affair with my best friend,</i>

47:43.125 --> 47:45.333
<i>and you didn't think</i>
<i>I had the right to know.</i>

47:45.416 --> 47:46.458
<i>Look, Beth…</i>

47:47.625 --> 47:49.708
<i>How long was it going on for?</i>

47:50.791 --> 47:51.666
<i>Not long.</i>

47:53.708 --> 47:55.166
<i>Uh… a few months.</i>

47:55.750 --> 47:58.166
<i>I guess she was trying to get back at me.</i>
<i>Tit for Tat.</i>

47:58.250 --> 47:59.125
<i>Wow.</i>

48:00.291 --> 48:01.208
<i>Wow.</i>

48:02.166 --> 48:03.916
<i>You know they had a thing at Uni.</i>

48:04.000 --> 48:06.958
<i>Yeah, yeah, a drunken one-night stand</i>
<i>at freshman week.</i>

48:07.041 --> 48:09.166
<i>-What are you saying?</i>
<i>-[Jay]</i> I'm not saying anything.

48:09.250 --> 48:10.333
<i>It's just, you know,</i>

48:10.416 --> 48:12.708
<i>maybe there</i>
<i>were some latent feelings on her part.</i>

48:18.083 --> 48:20.291
<i>[Beth] How could I have not seen it?</i>

48:22.291 --> 48:24.625
<i>We don't see what we don't want to see.</i>

48:27.916 --> 48:30.583
<i>I've been feeling so guilty for…</i>

48:32.291 --> 48:33.250
<i>for being…</i>

48:34.250 --> 48:36.250
<i>so unhappy. [cries]</i>

48:37.833 --> 48:40.291
<i>Like I'm not grateful enough</i>

48:41.041 --> 48:44.500
<i>for my life, for Aster.</i>

48:46.041 --> 48:48.541
<i>I was just too ashamed</i>

48:49.333 --> 48:52.416
<i>to look up and see what</i>
<i>was staring me in the face.</i>

48:57.291 --> 48:58.208
<i>Oh my God.</i>

49:02.125 --> 49:03.791
<i>What if she did drug me</i>

49:04.416 --> 49:06.916
<i>so I would sleep with someone</i>

49:07.500 --> 49:10.666
<i>or not know if I had or hadn't?</i>

49:11.666 --> 49:14.291
<i>Then she could get Rob to leave me.</i>

49:16.458 --> 49:18.416
<i>Do you think he could have killed Kate?</i>

49:19.541 --> 49:20.541
<i>Rob?</i>

49:20.625 --> 49:21.625
<i>[scoffs]</i>

49:21.708 --> 49:23.958
<i>Oh, God, no.</i>

49:24.458 --> 49:26.625
<i>And I spoke to him over the weekend.</i>

49:26.708 --> 49:29.000
<i>He was home with Aster.</i>

49:31.125 --> 49:33.291
<i>You never wondered if it was me?</i>

49:34.833 --> 49:35.666
<i>No.</i>

49:37.833 --> 49:39.041
<i>Too trusting, right?</i>

49:41.833 --> 49:43.458
<i>One thing I've learned,</i>

49:44.416 --> 49:45.875
<i>never trust people,</i>

49:46.708 --> 49:48.041
<i>only your instincts.</i>

49:50.083 --> 49:54.166
<i>Where I come from, </i>
<i>we say </i>Alalbek Daleelek.

49:55.958 --> 49:57.458
<i>Your heart is your guide.</i>

50:03.625 --> 50:04.458
<i>Zain.</i>

50:04.958 --> 50:05.833
<i>How did…</i>

50:08.875 --> 50:11.458
<i>How did your wife die?</i>

50:17.416 --> 50:19.083
<i>She was working in a clinic.</i>

50:21.791 --> 50:23.333
<i>There was a bombing. Uh…</i>

50:29.125 --> 50:30.666
<i>I was late to pick her up.</i>

50:44.666 --> 50:45.875
<i>It's not your fault.</i>

50:58.916 --> 51:00.375
<i>[somber music playing]</i>

51:04.416 --> 51:06.083
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

51:11.791 --> 51:13.291
<i>[Rob</i> <i>on phone]</i> 
You there? Hello? Hi?

51:13.958 --> 51:17.625
<i>Hey, um, I was putting Aster down.</i>
<i>Sorry, I got your message. You okay?</i>

51:19.041 --> 51:20.916
<i>I know, Rob.</i>

51:21.000 --> 51:22.333
<i>Know? Know what?</i>

51:23.416 --> 51:24.541
<i>[Beth] </i>About you and Kate.

51:27.000 --> 51:28.750
<i>-What about me and Kate?</i>
<i>-Stop!</i>

51:28.833 --> 51:30.750
<i>Beth, what are you talking about?</i>

51:30.833 --> 51:33.791
<i>That you were sleeping</i>
<i>with her for months.</i>

51:37.250 --> 51:39.750
<i>[chuckling nervously] Uh, what?</i>
<i>What you talking about?</i>

51:39.833 --> 51:44.500
<i>Stop treating me like an idiot.</i>
<i>I found the text messages on her phone.</i>

51:51.625 --> 51:52.541
<i>I… I…</i>

51:53.291 --> 51:54.125
<i>I…</i>

51:56.166 --> 51:58.291
<i>I don't know what to say. I'm sorry.</i>

51:59.416 --> 52:00.250
<i>I…</i>

52:00.750 --> 52:02.083
<i>It didn't mean anything.</i>

52:02.666 --> 52:05.416
<i>I only did it because we…</i>
<i>When was the last time we had sex?</i>

52:05.500 --> 52:09.458
<i>-You were depressed and I--</i>
-No! You do not get to blame this on me.

52:09.541 --> 52:13.000
<i>-No, I'm not blam… Look, I'm sorry--</i>
<i>-[Beth] </i>Stop apologizing!

52:14.625 --> 52:15.708
<i>Did you love her?</i>

52:17.291 --> 52:18.500
<i>Of course I didn't…</i>

52:19.375 --> 52:22.208
<i>Look, you've just got to come home.</i>
<i>We can't do this over the phone.</i>

52:22.291 --> 52:24.458
<i>I can't come home, Rob,</i>

52:24.541 --> 52:28.625
<i>because the police have taken my passport</i>
<i>because I'm sure they think I killed Kate.</i>

52:28.708 --> 52:32.083
<i>And if they find out about the affair,</i>
<i>they'll have a damn good reason too.</i>

52:33.083 --> 52:34.541
<i>[sighs]</i>

52:34.625 --> 52:36.250
<i>Beth, Beth, Beth, Beth.</i>

52:36.333 --> 52:38.166
<i>-I am so sorry.</i>
<i>-[Beth] </i>Just shut up.

52:39.041 --> 52:40.916
<i>[sniffling] I just want to see Aster.</i>

52:41.416 --> 52:43.000
<i>[line disconnects]</i>

52:46.791 --> 52:48.500
<i>[squawking]</i>

52:55.750 --> 52:57.000
<i>[knocking on door]</i>

52:58.375 --> 53:00.125
<i>[people speaking Croatian]</i>

53:01.125 --> 53:02.083
<i>[door closes]</i>

53:03.833 --> 53:07.083
<i>Beth Jenner, we're arresting you on</i>
<i>suspicion of the murder of Kate Thompson.</i>

53:07.583 --> 53:09.500
<i>[officer] Put your hands behind your back.</i>

53:09.583 --> 53:10.416
<i>What?</i>

53:11.500 --> 53:13.583
<i>For how long have you known Mr. Zakaria?</i>

53:17.500 --> 53:18.375
<i>Zain?</i>

53:21.458 --> 53:22.416
<i>A few days.</i>

53:23.291 --> 53:24.166
<i>[speaks Croatian]</i>

53:24.250 --> 53:25.291
<i>Why?</i>

53:25.375 --> 53:27.083
<i>How did the two of you meet?</i>

53:28.125 --> 53:29.500
<i>[Beth] He drives a taxi.</i>

53:30.333 --> 53:32.708
<i>He took me and Kate</i>
<i>to the bar on Friday night.</i>

53:33.375 --> 53:34.958
<i>He's been helping me look for her.</i>

53:35.041 --> 53:37.750
<i>Why didn't you tell us he was with you</i>
<i>when you confronted the escorts?</i>

53:37.833 --> 53:40.250
<i>Or that he physically</i>
<i>assaulted one of them?</i>

53:40.333 --> 53:41.750
<i>But they stole Kate's bag.</i>

53:41.833 --> 53:44.500
<i>He got them to admit it.</i>
<i>He got the bag back.</i>

53:44.583 --> 53:48.083
<i>Mr. Zakaria</i>
<i>is connected to organized crime.</i>

53:48.166 --> 53:50.541
<i>He's a member of an Albanian gang</i>

53:50.625 --> 53:53.875
<i>involved in human trafficking,</i>
<i>among other things.</i>

53:53.958 --> 53:55.541
<i>[officer speaks Croatian]</i>

53:56.541 --> 53:57.541
<i>What?</i>

53:57.625 --> 53:58.958
<i>You didn't know this about him?</i>

53:59.041 --> 54:03.166
<i>No. No, of course not.</i>
<i>What… What are you saying?</i>

54:03.250 --> 54:04.708
<i>He killed Kate.</i>

54:04.791 --> 54:06.083
<i>-No! No!</i>
<i>-[officer] Yes!</i>

54:06.166 --> 54:08.208
<i>-[Beth] He can't have.</i>
<i>-Yes. Yes.</i>

54:08.291 --> 54:09.166
<i>[speaks Croatian]</i>

54:09.250 --> 54:11.000
<i>[in English]</i> 
<i>And you hired him to do it.</i>

54:11.083 --> 54:12.916
<i>-What?</i>
<i>-He's also been arrested.</i>

54:13.000 --> 54:15.416
<i>This is insane! This is insane!</i>

54:15.500 --> 54:18.875
<i>How do you… You can't possibly think</i>
<i>I had anything to do with this!</i>

54:18.958 --> 54:21.208
<i>Please! Why would I want Kate dead?</i>

54:21.291 --> 54:23.750
<i>Because she was having an affair</i>
<i>with your husband.</i>

54:25.916 --> 54:26.958
<i>-[cries]</i>
<i>-[Kovac] Oh.</i>

54:27.666 --> 54:29.208
<i>You didn't think we'd find out.</i>

54:29.291 --> 54:31.333
<i>I only found out yesterday.</i>

54:34.291 --> 54:36.500
<i>Did you talk to Jay?</i>

54:36.583 --> 54:38.583
<i>Jay has known about it for months.</i>

54:38.666 --> 54:41.041
<i>We are speaking to him later today.</i>

54:42.708 --> 54:44.250
<i>[sighs, sniffles]</i>

54:45.083 --> 54:47.000
<i>I want a lawyer. [sniffles]</i>

54:47.625 --> 54:49.083
<i>Can I have a lawyer?</i>

54:49.166 --> 54:52.625
<i>Just because they haven't charged you</i>
<i>doesn't mean they won't.</i>

54:52.708 --> 54:55.458
<i>It is only because they don't</i>
<i>have enough evidence yet.</i>

54:55.541 --> 54:59.166
<i>They were hoping they could press you</i>
<i>on your connection to Mr. Zacharia,</i>

54:59.250 --> 55:00.750
<i>and you'd confess.</i>

55:00.833 --> 55:02.291
<i>To what?</i>

55:02.375 --> 55:03.666
<i>I didn't do anything.</i>

55:04.625 --> 55:05.708
<i>[sighs]</i>

55:07.791 --> 55:11.500
<i>Call me next time before you say anything</i>
<i>to incriminate yourself.</i>

55:13.125 --> 55:14.000
<i>[exhales sharply]</i>

55:19.250 --> 55:20.291
<i>[sighs]</i>

55:34.166 --> 55:35.250
<i>[gasps]</i>

55:35.833 --> 55:37.875
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

55:37.958 --> 55:39.458
<i>What are you doing here?</i>

55:39.541 --> 55:41.041
<i>Your landlord let me in.</i>

55:41.791 --> 55:43.125
<i>I needed to see you.</i>

55:44.666 --> 55:46.625
<i>They told me you'd been arrested.</i>

55:47.250 --> 55:48.375
<i>[Zain] They let me go.</i>

55:49.750 --> 55:53.166
<i>I was driving all Friday night</i>
<i>until Saturday morning.</i>

55:53.250 --> 55:55.041
<i>The app tracks everything.</i>

55:55.750 --> 55:56.666
<i>They said…</i>

55:58.166 --> 56:01.500
<i>you have links</i>
<i>to an Albanian criminal gang.</i>

56:04.041 --> 56:05.708
<i>You think I killed Kate?</i>

56:06.291 --> 56:07.375
<i>I don't know.</i>

56:07.458 --> 56:09.500
<i>I don't know who to believe.</i>

56:15.541 --> 56:19.375
<i>I saved the life of a boy</i>
<i>who'd been hit with shrapnel in the leg.</i>

56:19.458 --> 56:22.625
<i>His father has connections</i>
<i>to an Albanian people-smuggling ring.</i>

56:23.583 --> 56:27.625
<i>He got me out of Aleppo,</i>
<i>crossed the border into Turkey then here.</i>

56:27.708 --> 56:29.375
<i>Helped secure me a visa.</i>

56:31.750 --> 56:33.833
<i>So you don't work for this person?</i>

56:35.083 --> 56:35.916
<i>No.</i>

56:37.291 --> 56:39.708
<i>How do I know you're telling me the truth?</i>

56:40.416 --> 56:43.208
<i>[in Arabic] Your heart is your guide.</i>

56:54.000 --> 56:56.000
<i>[birds chirping]</i>

56:58.208 --> 57:00.833
<i>[Beth] </i>You can't possibly think
I had anything to do with this.

57:00.916 --> 57:02.208
<i>Why would I want Kate dead?</i>

57:02.291 --> 57:05.083
<i>Because she was having an affair</i>
<i>with your husband.</i>

57:05.166 --> 57:07.166
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

57:19.166 --> 57:21.166
<i>[music continues]</i>

57:29.666 --> 57:30.708
<i>[Beth] </i>So what?

57:31.250 --> 57:34.083
<i>My husband was having an affair</i>
<i>with my best friend.</i>

57:34.166 --> 57:36.083
<i>You didn't think I had the right to know?</i>

57:36.166 --> 57:38.083
<i>[music intensifies]</i>

57:46.958 --> 57:48.958
<i>[ominous music playing]</i>

57:49.791 --> 57:50.833
<i>[exhales]</i>

57:56.250 --> 57:57.416
<i>[Beth] Oh my God.</i>

57:58.666 --> 58:00.666
<i>[ominous music continues]</i>

58:06.583 --> 58:08.583
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

58:18.125 --> 58:19.250
<i>[knocks]</i>

58:20.208 --> 58:21.041
<i>Hello.</i>

58:24.000 --> 58:26.041
<i>[foreboding music playing]</i>

58:40.708 --> 58:42.500
<i>Are you looking for something?</i>

58:43.625 --> 58:44.791
<i>Oh, uh…</i>

58:45.541 --> 58:47.166
<i>Uh, takeout menus.</i>

58:47.750 --> 58:48.750
<i>I'm hungry.</i>

58:49.583 --> 58:51.083
<i>All the menus are online.</i>

58:51.708 --> 58:54.166
<i>Uh, my cell data ran out.</i>

58:55.833 --> 58:58.000
<i>Could I get the Wi-Fi password?</i>

59:01.583 --> 59:02.791
<i>-Excuse me.</i>
<i>-[Beth] Yeah.</i>

59:04.500 --> 59:06.041
<i>[objects clattering]</i>

59:11.125 --> 59:14.041
<i>[Sebastian] What happened with the police?</i>
<i>They let you go.</i>

59:15.333 --> 59:16.166
<i>Yeah.</i>

59:18.208 --> 59:21.000
<i>[Sebastian] And how much longer</i>
<i>do you think you'll be staying here?</i>

59:23.041 --> 59:24.791
<i>Um, I… I don't know.</i>

59:24.875 --> 59:27.208
<i>-Are you going out somewhere?</i>
<i>-[Sebastian] Yes.</i>

59:28.958 --> 59:32.583
<i>A screening for a movie </i>
<i>I supervised the music for.</i>

59:35.125 --> 59:36.083
<i>Hmm.</i>

59:36.708 --> 59:38.291
<i>-Goodbye, then.</i>
<i>-[keys jingling]</i>

59:41.625 --> 59:42.708
<i>[door opens]</i>

59:43.875 --> 59:44.791
<i>[door closes]</i>

59:46.833 --> 59:48.833
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

59:53.375 --> 59:54.625
<i>[door unlocking]</i>

59:55.625 --> 59:56.625
<i>[door creaking]</i>

1:00:16.125 --> 1:00:18.125
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

1:00:22.250 --> 1:00:23.333
<i>[gasps]</i>

1:00:31.083 --> 1:00:32.000
<i>What?</i>

1:00:32.958 --> 1:00:34.291
<i>[speaking indistinctly]</i>

1:00:38.500 --> 1:00:40.583
<i>[Beth] Oh my Jesus Christ.</i>

1:00:45.208 --> 1:00:46.291
<i>Oh my God.</i>

1:00:48.250 --> 1:00:50.708
<i>-[footage whirring]</i>
<i>-You're filming everything.</i>

1:00:54.541 --> 1:00:56.125
<i>Did you film Friday?</i>

1:01:00.958 --> 1:01:02.333
<i>Come on, come on, come on.</i>

1:01:02.416 --> 1:01:04.375
<i>[music intensifies]</i>

1:01:09.041 --> 1:01:11.041
<i>[Beth] </i>Whoa! Oh my God.

1:01:11.125 --> 1:01:12.541
<i>-[Kate] </i>Yeah, right?
<i>-[Beth chuckles]</i>

1:01:12.625 --> 1:01:15.875
<i>-</i>Well, thanks. Are you sure?
<i>-[Kate] </i>Yeah, no, for sure. Come on.

1:01:15.958 --> 1:01:16.791
<i>[Beth chuckles]</i>

1:01:17.375 --> 1:01:18.333
<i>[Kate] </i>Fine.

1:01:25.583 --> 1:01:27.291
<i>-[Mateo] </i>Here we go.
<i>-[Kate] </i>Watch your step.

1:01:27.375 --> 1:01:29.208
<i>[Mateo] </i>I'm watching my step.

1:01:29.291 --> 1:01:31.791
<i>Somebody's gonna have</i>
<i>a beautiful night of sleep.</i>

1:01:31.875 --> 1:01:32.916
<i>Beth.</i>

1:01:33.000 --> 1:01:34.833
<i>What happened to you?</i>

1:01:34.916 --> 1:01:35.833
<i>[Mateo grunts]</i>

1:01:35.916 --> 1:01:38.291
<i>Let's get you ready for bed. Yeah. Whoa.</i>

1:01:38.375 --> 1:01:42.416
<i>[footage whirring]</i>

1:01:42.500 --> 1:01:43.583
<i>[mouse clicks]</i>

1:01:51.125 --> 1:01:53.125
<i>[Kate laughing]</i>

1:01:54.916 --> 1:01:56.625
<i>Come on, join in.</i>

1:01:56.708 --> 1:01:57.708
<i>[Luka] </i>Whoo!

1:01:58.416 --> 1:01:59.416
<i>Very good.</i>

1:01:59.500 --> 1:02:00.416
<i>[Kate] </i>Hot tub.

1:02:01.458 --> 1:02:02.750
<i>Whoo-hoo!</i>

1:02:02.833 --> 1:02:04.833
<i>Hot tub on the balcony.</i>

1:02:05.625 --> 1:02:07.333
<i>Oh yeah, strip down.</i>

1:02:07.416 --> 1:02:08.375
<i>[laughs]</i>

1:02:10.333 --> 1:02:11.375
<i>[Kate] </i>Whoo!

1:02:16.083 --> 1:02:17.125
<i>[mouse clicks]</i>

1:02:17.708 --> 1:02:19.041
<i>Don't you go anywhere.</i>

1:02:19.125 --> 1:02:20.333
<i>Don't take too long.</i>

1:02:21.416 --> 1:02:22.500
<i>See you, beautiful.</i>

1:02:22.583 --> 1:02:23.583
<i>[laughs]</i>

1:02:29.125 --> 1:02:30.750
<i>[men speaking Croatian]</i>

1:02:37.125 --> 1:02:38.833
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

1:02:44.083 --> 1:02:45.500
<i>Son of a bitch!</i>

1:02:46.250 --> 1:02:47.333
<i>Bitch!</i>

1:02:53.166 --> 1:02:54.375
<i>-Ahh!</i>
-[glass shatters]

1:02:56.375 --> 1:02:58.250
<i>[suspenseful music continues]</i>

1:03:02.583 --> 1:03:04.000
<i>[music intensifies]</i>

1:03:19.416 --> 1:03:20.958
<i>[mouse clicking]</i>

1:03:30.666 --> 1:03:32.250
<i>[Beth] Who's that with her?</i>

1:03:33.250 --> 1:03:34.500
<i>[inaudible]</i>

1:03:35.125 --> 1:03:36.000
<i>[mouse clicks]</i>

1:03:38.583 --> 1:03:40.125
<i>-[door opens]</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

1:03:41.041 --> 1:03:42.000
<i>[door closes]</i>

1:03:45.583 --> 1:03:46.541
<i>[doorknob clicks]</i>

1:03:50.708 --> 1:03:51.958
<i>-[thuds]</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

1:03:52.041 --> 1:03:53.583
<i>[groaning]</i>

1:03:54.833 --> 1:03:57.583
<i>-[Beth] No!</i>
<i>-No! Stop! It's not what you think!</i>

1:03:57.666 --> 1:03:59.166
<i>It's for security!</i>

1:03:59.250 --> 1:04:00.458
<i>People have parties!</i>

1:04:00.541 --> 1:04:03.208
<i>You're taping people</i>
<i>in the shower having sex!</i>

1:04:03.291 --> 1:04:05.791
<i>And you knew what happened to Kate</i>
<i>this whole time.</i>

1:04:05.875 --> 1:04:07.416
<i>You could have told the police.</i>

1:04:07.500 --> 1:04:10.250
<i>You told them</i>
<i>about my husband's affair, didn't you?</i>

1:04:10.333 --> 1:04:11.500
<i>What are you doing?</i>

1:04:11.583 --> 1:04:14.208
<i>What is that? No. Don't delete them.</i>

1:04:14.291 --> 1:04:15.708
<i>It's evidence! No!</i>

1:04:16.916 --> 1:04:17.833
<i>[Sebastian] Stop!</i>

1:04:19.000 --> 1:04:19.875
<i>Oh gosh.</i>

1:04:19.958 --> 1:04:21.541
<i>[panting]</i>

1:04:22.833 --> 1:04:24.833
<i>[foreboding music playing]</i>

1:04:31.291 --> 1:04:33.291
<i>[ominous music playing]</i>

1:04:36.958 --> 1:04:38.708
<i>[buzzer buzzing]</i>

1:04:40.625 --> 1:04:42.291
<i>-[moans]</i>
<i>-[screams]</i>

1:04:45.458 --> 1:04:46.375
<i>[Beth] Oh!</i>

1:04:47.250 --> 1:04:48.458
<i>[keys jingling]</i>

1:04:54.583 --> 1:04:55.416
<i>Help!</i>

1:04:56.083 --> 1:04:57.208
<i>-[Zain] Beth.</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

1:04:58.250 --> 1:04:59.625
<i>Oh. [groans]</i>

1:04:59.708 --> 1:05:01.458
<i>-[Sebastian] Wait!</i>
<i>-[Beth] Let's go.</i>

1:05:01.541 --> 1:05:02.708
<i>[Zain] What happened?</i>

1:05:03.583 --> 1:05:06.750
<i>[Sebastian] Stop, you don't understand!</i>
<i>Stop. I can explain.</i>

1:05:06.833 --> 1:05:08.333
<i>-[Beth] Go! Now! Go!</i>
<i>-[tires screeching]</i>

1:05:08.416 --> 1:05:10.375
<i>[Sebastian] Beth! Come back! Come back!</i>

1:05:10.458 --> 1:05:12.458
<i>He… He deleted all the videos.</i>

1:05:13.083 --> 1:05:15.250
<i>He's gonna tell the police I attacked him.</i>

1:05:15.750 --> 1:05:18.083
<i>Oh my God, this is a nightmare.</i>

1:05:18.875 --> 1:05:20.083
<i>Listen.</i>

1:05:20.166 --> 1:05:21.750
<i>We'll find out where Kate went,</i>

1:05:21.833 --> 1:05:24.125
<i>then we can hopefully find out</i>
<i>who brought her home.</i>

1:05:24.208 --> 1:05:27.333
<i>Then we can go to the police.</i>
<i>We will explain. It will be okay.</i>

1:05:27.416 --> 1:05:28.291
<i>Trust me.</i>

1:05:31.916 --> 1:05:34.333
<i>[tires screeching]</i>

1:05:37.916 --> 1:05:39.583
<i>I gave him the license number.</i>

1:05:40.208 --> 1:05:41.750
<i>Driver is on his way.</i>

1:05:43.333 --> 1:05:44.250
<i>Did I hurt you?</i>

1:05:45.875 --> 1:05:47.041
<i>You hurt your hand?</i>

1:05:47.125 --> 1:05:48.000
<i>A little.</i>

1:05:49.041 --> 1:05:52.375
<i>Throat, balls, eyes.</i>

1:05:53.083 --> 1:05:54.125
<i>Soft targets.</i>

1:05:54.625 --> 1:05:57.041
<i>Okay, I'll remember that for next time.</i>

1:05:57.833 --> 1:05:59.333
<i>[newsreader speaking Croatian]</i>

1:06:00.250 --> 1:06:01.541
<i>What does that mean?</i>

1:06:03.708 --> 1:06:05.958
<i>They say you're a suspect</i>
<i>in Kate's murder.</i>

1:06:09.541 --> 1:06:10.875
<i>You speak English?</i>

1:06:10.958 --> 1:06:11.833
<i>Very little.</i>

1:06:13.333 --> 1:06:17.166
<i>You picked up a woman</i>
<i>early Saturday morning around 3:00.</i>

1:06:17.250 --> 1:06:20.083
<i>-She's my height, blonde hair.</i>
<i>-[Zain] On Jerina Street.</i>

1:06:23.083 --> 1:06:24.083
<i>[in Croatian] She's dead.</i>

1:06:24.916 --> 1:06:25.875
<i>She was murdered.</i>

1:06:26.625 --> 1:06:28.875
<i>Where did you take her?</i>

1:06:30.083 --> 1:06:32.750
<i>We just need</i>
<i>to know where you took her. That's all.</i>

1:06:33.250 --> 1:06:36.875
<i>She made me follow these two men.</i>
<i>She said they stole her bag.</i>

1:06:36.958 --> 1:06:38.875
<i>I lost them on a one-way street.</i>

1:06:38.958 --> 1:06:41.000
<i>[in English] What's he saying?</i>
<i>Where'd you take her?</i>

1:06:41.083 --> 1:06:42.750
<i>[speaks Croatian]</i>

1:06:44.250 --> 1:06:45.083
<i>Where?</i>

1:06:45.833 --> 1:06:47.000
<i>The police station.</i>

1:06:52.041 --> 1:06:52.875
<i>Thank you.</i>

1:06:55.291 --> 1:06:57.083
<i>[Beth] If Kate reported her bag stolen,</i>

1:06:57.166 --> 1:06:59.458
<i>why wasn't there a record of it</i>
<i>when I reported her missing?</i>

1:06:59.541 --> 1:07:00.916
<i>Maybe it never got filed.</i>

1:07:01.000 --> 1:07:03.083
<i>Pavic didn't file my report either.</i>

1:07:03.166 --> 1:07:05.291
<i>[man speaks Croatian]</i>

1:07:07.500 --> 1:07:09.000
<i>We need to get out of here.</i>

1:07:12.041 --> 1:07:13.708
<i>[tires screeching]</i>

1:07:13.791 --> 1:07:15.041
<i>[sirens wailing]</i>

1:07:24.041 --> 1:07:25.125
<i>Come on!</i>

1:07:25.708 --> 1:07:28.166
<i>[Kovac] Beth! Don't leave!</i>
<i>We just want to talk.</i>

1:07:28.750 --> 1:07:29.791
<i>[Pavic] Stop!</i>

1:07:29.875 --> 1:07:31.666
<i>[exhilarating music playing]</i>

1:07:31.750 --> 1:07:33.375
<i>[Pavic yells in Croatian]</i>

1:07:37.666 --> 1:07:38.666
<i>[Kovac] Beth!</i>

1:07:39.166 --> 1:07:40.708
<i>[Pavic] Stop! Right now!</i>

1:07:43.625 --> 1:07:45.041
<i>[speaks Croatian]</i>

1:07:52.041 --> 1:07:54.041
<i>[speaking Croatian]</i>

1:07:54.125 --> 1:07:55.208
<i>[in English] Stop it!</i>

1:07:57.083 --> 1:07:58.333
<i>[Kovac speaking Croatian]</i>

1:07:58.416 --> 1:07:59.250
<i>Come on.</i>

1:08:02.083 --> 1:08:04.500
<i>[Pavic speaks Croatian]</i>

1:08:05.416 --> 1:08:06.458
<i>[Kovac] Stop!</i>

1:08:07.083 --> 1:08:09.208
<i>-[Kovac speaking indistinctly]</i>
<i>-[panting]</i>

1:08:11.708 --> 1:08:12.541
<i>His car.</i>

1:08:13.208 --> 1:08:14.333
<i>The cop's car.</i>

1:08:14.416 --> 1:08:17.333
<i>I saw the sticker in the security footage.</i>

1:08:17.416 --> 1:08:20.291
<i>He must've driven Kate home</i>
<i>after she reported her bag stolen.</i>

1:08:20.375 --> 1:08:22.083
<i>Why didn't he say anything?</i>

1:08:24.375 --> 1:08:26.750
<i>Oh my God. Oh my God. Oh my God.</i>

1:08:28.875 --> 1:08:31.458
<i>It was him. It was him.</i>

1:08:32.291 --> 1:08:33.291
<i>It was Pavic.</i>

1:08:34.625 --> 1:08:35.750
<i>[Zain] Call your lawyer.</i>

1:08:35.833 --> 1:08:38.083
<i>-Make her meet you.</i>
<i>-[Beth] Wait. Where are you going?</i>

1:08:38.166 --> 1:08:40.166
<i>-Don't worry about me.</i>
<i>-[Beth] No.</i>

1:08:40.250 --> 1:08:41.333
<i>You'll get in trouble.</i>

1:08:44.000 --> 1:08:45.458
<i>[Zain] Go! Go! Go!</i>

1:08:45.541 --> 1:08:46.958
<i>[tense music playing]</i>

1:08:49.833 --> 1:08:52.708
<i>[speaking Croatian]</i>

1:08:53.416 --> 1:08:54.666
<i>[speaks Croatian]</i>

1:08:55.333 --> 1:08:56.375
<i>[Zain, in English] It's him!</i>

1:08:56.916 --> 1:08:58.625
<i>Believe me it's him.</i>
<i>It's the cop who did it.</i>

1:08:58.708 --> 1:09:01.125
<i>-[Kovac] What're you talking about?</i>
<i>-[Zain] We saw the footage.</i>

1:09:01.208 --> 1:09:02.375
<i>[Kovac] What do you mean?</i>

1:09:02.875 --> 1:09:04.875
<i>[tense music continues]</i>

1:09:13.833 --> 1:09:15.083
<i>[Beth panting]</i>

1:09:16.333 --> 1:09:18.083
<i>[in Croatian] Where did she go?</i>

1:09:37.416 --> 1:09:38.375
<i>[speaking Croatian]</i>

1:09:38.458 --> 1:09:39.458
<i>[in English] Stop!</i>

1:09:40.458 --> 1:09:41.750
<i>You're under arrest.</i>

1:09:41.833 --> 1:09:43.000
<i>It was you.</i>

1:09:43.916 --> 1:09:45.541
<i>You killed her.</i>

1:09:45.625 --> 1:09:46.458
<i>What?</i>

1:09:47.416 --> 1:09:49.083
<i>[Beth] You hit on her, didn't you?</i>

1:09:49.166 --> 1:09:50.250
<i>Shut up.</i>

1:09:50.333 --> 1:09:53.500
<i>My God, you did!</i>
<i>You hit on her, and she rejected you!</i>

1:09:53.583 --> 1:09:54.416
<i>She was a slut!</i>

1:09:54.500 --> 1:09:56.791
<i>That's what men call women</i>
<i>who won't sleep with them!</i>

1:09:56.875 --> 1:09:59.041
<i>-Shut your mouth! Shut up!</i>
<i>-No! No!</i>

1:09:59.125 --> 1:10:00.708
<i>Shut your mouth!</i>

1:10:00.791 --> 1:10:02.708
<i>Pavic, stop! Stop it!</i>

1:10:02.791 --> 1:10:03.708
<i>[yelps]</i>

1:10:03.791 --> 1:10:05.250
<i>-[screams]</i>
<i>-[body thuds]</i>

1:10:10.833 --> 1:10:12.625
<i>[Beth breathing heavily]</i>

1:10:17.750 --> 1:10:18.916
<i>[crying]</i>

1:10:38.833 --> 1:10:39.666
<i>Hi.</i>

1:10:40.625 --> 1:10:42.000
<i>Sorry for the wait.</i>

1:10:43.333 --> 1:10:44.541
<i>How are you feeling?</i>

1:10:48.500 --> 1:10:50.666
<i>We found security footage.</i>

1:10:50.750 --> 1:10:52.333
<i>A camera on the boardwalk.</i>

1:10:52.416 --> 1:10:55.750
<i>And we recovered</i>
<i>some of your landlord's footage.</i>

1:10:57.000 --> 1:10:59.625
<i>I'm so sorry I doubted you.</i>
<i>You were right.</i>

1:10:59.708 --> 1:11:03.125
<i>Pavic drove Kate home</i>
<i>after she reported her bag stolen.</i>

1:11:03.708 --> 1:11:06.083
<i>We think he did make a pass at her.</i>

1:11:07.500 --> 1:11:08.833
<i>When she rejected him,</i>

1:11:09.458 --> 1:11:10.791
<i>he took it badly.</i>

1:11:13.000 --> 1:11:14.416
<i>[Beth sighs, sniffles]</i>

1:11:15.666 --> 1:11:17.833
<i>So he… he killed her.</i>

1:11:22.166 --> 1:11:24.250
<i>[Kovac] Based on the autopsy results,</i>

1:11:25.250 --> 1:11:29.583
<i>we can safely assume</i>
<i>Pavic hit her over the back of the head,</i>

1:11:31.166 --> 1:11:33.416
<i>and then dumped her body in the harbor</i>

1:11:34.208 --> 1:11:35.875
<i>while she was still alive.</i>

1:11:37.375 --> 1:11:38.208
<i>Why?</i>

1:11:39.375 --> 1:11:40.208
<i>I…</i>

1:11:42.416 --> 1:11:43.875
<i>I… I don't understand.</i>

1:11:44.458 --> 1:11:46.708
<i>Pavic used to work vice. [sighs]</i>

1:11:48.875 --> 1:11:50.041
<i>Several women</i>

1:11:51.125 --> 1:11:54.208
<i>he arrested for sex work</i>
<i>claimed he assaulted them.</i>

1:11:54.291 --> 1:11:56.166
<i>Internal Affairs investigated it,</i>

1:11:56.250 --> 1:11:59.750
<i>but the women</i>
<i>all withdrew their statements.</i>

1:12:02.541 --> 1:12:04.208
<i>We think he threatened them.</i>

1:12:04.291 --> 1:12:05.541
<i>IA couldn't fire him,</i>

1:12:05.625 --> 1:12:09.500
<i>so unfortunately, they moved him over</i>
<i>to the tourist division.</i>

1:12:12.916 --> 1:12:14.625
<i>She didn't deserve this.</i>

1:12:16.583 --> 1:12:18.041
<i>-No.</i>
<i>-[Beth sniffles]</i>

1:12:18.583 --> 1:12:19.458
<i>I…</i>

1:12:20.166 --> 1:12:21.583
<i>I ordered a search warrant</i>

1:12:21.666 --> 1:12:24.458
<i>on Luka and Mateo's apartment</i>
<i>and workplace too.</i>

1:12:25.375 --> 1:12:26.458
<i>We found ketamine.</i>

1:12:26.541 --> 1:12:29.791
<i>They've been drugging the women</i>
<i>who hired them then robbing them.</i>

1:12:30.291 --> 1:12:31.958
<i>They drugged Kate too,</i>

1:12:32.041 --> 1:12:34.833
<i>but the cocaine</i>
<i>in her system counteracted it.</i>

1:12:36.291 --> 1:12:37.541
<i>We are charging them.</i>

1:12:37.625 --> 1:12:38.625
<i>[sniffles]</i>

1:12:41.000 --> 1:12:42.500
<i>So I'm free to go then.</i>

1:12:43.541 --> 1:12:44.666
<i>[Kovac] Wait a second.</i>

1:12:47.625 --> 1:12:48.833
<i>[drawer opens]</i>

1:12:55.250 --> 1:12:58.666
<i>In case you want</i>
<i>to press charges against your landlord.</i>

1:12:58.750 --> 1:13:00.250
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:13:10.916 --> 1:13:12.916
<i>[seagulls cawing]</i>

1:13:24.500 --> 1:13:25.666
<i>Are you okay?</i>

1:13:30.750 --> 1:13:31.666
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:13:40.458 --> 1:13:41.375
<i>Thank you.</i>

1:13:41.875 --> 1:13:43.458
<i>[soft music playing]</i>

1:13:47.000 --> 1:13:48.208
<i>[sniffles]</i>

1:14:02.083 --> 1:14:04.083
<i>[speaking indistinctly]</i>

1:14:05.875 --> 1:14:06.958
<i>[phone dings]</i>

1:14:26.208 --> 1:14:27.416
<i>[knocking]</i>

1:14:29.083 --> 1:14:30.166
<i>[shushing]</i>

1:14:30.708 --> 1:14:31.541
<i>Sorry, it's…</i>

1:14:32.291 --> 1:14:33.541
<i>a bit of a mess.</i>

1:14:34.916 --> 1:14:38.291
<i>Uh, I just put the kettle on.</i>
<i>Do you want to stay for a cuppa?</i>

1:14:38.875 --> 1:14:40.083
<i>I'm good.</i>

1:14:40.166 --> 1:14:44.166
<i>Uh, I packed clothes</i>
<i>and Ernie the sheep in the bag.</i>

1:14:44.250 --> 1:14:45.750
<i>I… I didn't bring diapers.</i>

1:14:45.833 --> 1:14:47.250
<i>I figured you had those.</i>

1:14:49.208 --> 1:14:51.583
<i>I can pop out and get some. No worries.</i>

1:14:51.666 --> 1:14:52.500
<i>Okay.</i>

1:14:53.458 --> 1:14:57.375
<i>Hey, there's this kids' art thing</i>
<i>at the park tomorrow.</i>

1:14:57.458 --> 1:15:00.166
<i>I was thinking</i>
<i>of taking Aster if you fancy joining us.</i>

1:15:01.125 --> 1:15:04.500
<i>Maybe we could have lunch after</i>
<i>at Georgio's, the three of us.</i>

1:15:08.041 --> 1:15:08.875
<i>Please.</i>

1:15:12.833 --> 1:15:13.875
<i>-Beth.</i>
<i>-[Beth grunts]</i>

1:15:14.750 --> 1:15:16.208
<i>[kettle whistling]</i>

1:15:29.458 --> 1:15:30.416
<i>Uh…</i>

1:15:31.625 --> 1:15:34.791
<i>You know, uh, I think you might</i>
<i>have my spare car key.</i>

1:15:36.583 --> 1:15:40.708
<i>Yeah, it's probably</i>
<i>in the bowl in the hallway</i>

1:15:40.791 --> 1:15:41.958
<i>or in my jacket.</i>

1:15:45.541 --> 1:15:47.541
<i>[objects clattering]</i>

1:15:51.916 --> 1:15:52.833
<i>[Beth sighs]</i>

1:15:55.208 --> 1:15:56.708
<i>[rattling]</i>

1:16:00.541 --> 1:16:02.208
<i>[eerie music playing]</i>

1:16:06.208 --> 1:16:08.041
<i>[music intensifies]</i>

1:16:10.250 --> 1:16:11.083
<i>Oh!</i>

1:16:11.166 --> 1:16:12.625
<i>Oh my God, I'm so sorry.</i>

1:16:12.708 --> 1:16:14.083
<i>-[chuckles]</i>
<i>-[Beth grunts]</i>

1:16:15.125 --> 1:16:16.875
<i>I… I got it online.</i>

1:16:16.958 --> 1:16:18.208
<i>I can send it back.</i>

1:16:22.500 --> 1:16:24.000
<i>-[Rob] You all right?</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

1:16:26.916 --> 1:16:28.250
<i>You find the key?</i>

1:16:29.500 --> 1:16:31.500
<i>[tense music playing]</i>

1:16:35.791 --> 1:16:36.791
<i>Uh…</i>

1:16:36.875 --> 1:16:38.333
